%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Most%20Americans%20who%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20next%20year%20can't%20afford%20a%2020%25%20down%20payment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22long%20and%20foster%20for%20sale%20sign%20under%20contract%20is%20in%20front%20of%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63d2f347b1f17f001805dd85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20been%20an%20uptick%20in%20those%20starting%20the%20homebuying%20process%2C%20per%20Redfin's%20data.%3Cp%3ESAUL%20LOEB%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20Americans%20who%20plan%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20next%20year%20can't%20afford%20a%20down%20payment%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20median%20prospective%20homebuyer%20has%20a%20total%20of%20%2429%2C000%20in%20all%20accounts%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20for%20an%208%25%20down%20payment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20aren't%20enough%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20for%20everyone%20who%20wants%20to%20buy%20one%2C%20Zillow%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20who%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20can't%20afford%20a%20typical%20down%20payment%20of%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20median%20prospective%20homebuyer%20has%20a%20total%20of%20%2429%2C000%20in%20their%20savings%2C%20checking%2C%20investments%20and%20retirement%20accounts%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow's%202023%20Consumer%20Housing%20Trends%20Report.%20This%20amounts%20to%208%25%20of%20the%20typical%20cost%20of%20a%20home%2C%20which%20Zillow%20estimated%20cost%20nearly%20%24350%2C000%20as%20of%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20third%20of%20people%20who%20took%20out%20a%20mortgage%20in%202023%20drew%20from%20their%20retirement%20funds%2C%20Manny%20Garcia%2C%20Zillow's%20senior%20population%20scientist%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20harder%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20have%20much%20cash%20on%20hand%20to%20secure%20one%20of%20the%20limited%20amount%20of%20homes%20available.%20Of%20the%20nearly%20quarter%20of%20Americans%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20purchase%20a%20home%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20only%2037%25%20told%20Zillow%20that%20they%20currently%20had%20saved%20up%20enough%20for%20a%20down%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20about%2054%20million%20Americans%20who%20said%20they%20intend%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20%E2%80%94%20that%20represents%2034%20million%20unique%20households%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcia%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20know%20from%20historic%20data%20on%20home%20sales%20that%20no%20more%20than%206%20million%20homes%20have%20come%20on%20the%20market%20in%20any%20given%20recent%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrankly%20there%20just%20aren't%20enough%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20for%20everyone%20who%20wants%20to%20buy%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDown%20payment%20requirements%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20range%20from%200%25%20to%20more%20than%2020%25%2C%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20and%20in%20America's%2020%20biggest%20cities%2C%20a%2020%25%20down%20payment%20ranges%20from%20%2439%2C859%20in%20Oklahoma%20City%20to%20%24260%2C849%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZillow%20found%20just%20over%20half%20(56%25)%20of%20prospective%20mortgage%20buyers%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20put%20down%20less%20than%2020%25%20on%20the%20home%20they%20intend%20to%20buy%20and%20among%20prospective%20buyers%20that%20say%20they%20have%20saved%20up%20enough%20for%20a%20down%20payment%2C%20that%20amount%20is%20higher%20%E2%80%93%20typically%20%2459%2C000%20(enough%20for%20about%2017%25%20down).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingwire.com%2Farticles%2Fbanks-report-tighter-lending-standards-weaker-demand-for-mortgages-and-helocs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebanks%20are%20tightening%20qualifications%20for%20mortgages%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%202023%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20people%20who%20successfully%20got%20a%20mortgage%20put%20down%2020%25%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20home%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow.%20That%20is%20more%20than%20it%20has%20been%20in%20past%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETotal%20down%20payments%20are%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20to%20consider%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-affordability-home-price-us-43-income-mortgage-rates-increase-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomes%20to%20affordability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20someone%20scores%20a%20mortgage%20with%20a%20lower%20down%20payment%2C%20monthly%20costs%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20have%20a%20pretty%20good%20monthly%20payment%20on%203%25%20a%20year%20or%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20that's%20no%20longer%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcia%20said%20of%20rising%20mortgage%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20bills%20are%20important%20to%20consider%2C%20according%20to%20Insider's%20personal%20finance%20desk%2C%20which%20suggests%20that%20homebuyers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsteps-when-budgeting-for-our-house-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elive%20off%20one%20paycheck%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20they%20consider%20monthly%20expenses%20when%20deciding%20if%20a%20home%20is%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20conducted%20by%20Zillow%20Group%20Population%20Science%20of%20more%20than%2011%2C800%20prospective%20buyers%20nationally%20between%20April%20and%20July%202023%2C%20and%20defined%20%26quot%3Bprospective%20buyers%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20household%20decision%20makers%2018%20years%20of%20age%20or%20older%20who%20intend%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-americans-cant-afford-a-down-payment-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695203161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6509d979bf943d00195bb107%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-americans-cant-afford-a-down-payment-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20median%20prospective%20homebuyer%20has%20a%20total%20of%20%2429%2C000%20in%20their%20savings%2C%20checking%2C%20investments%20and%20retirement%20accounts%2C%20Zillow%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kneubauer%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Neubauer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-americans-cant-afford-a-down-payment-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20Timing%2C%20Small%20Fine'%3A%20How%20Anil%20Ambani's%20Relevance%20Diminished%20in%20the%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F04145423%2FAnil-PTI.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20September%2012%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20penalised%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%20with%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20and%20its%20three%20promoters%20Rs%206.5%20lakh%2C%20due%20to%20violations%20of%20some%20regulations%20and%20its%20failure%20to%20disclose%20the%20adverse%20findings%20of%20a%20forensic%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmoney-and-banking%2Fsebi-penalises-reliance-home-finance-for-violating-lodr-regulations-and-concealing-forensic-report-findings%2Farticle67300509.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20marked%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20that%20had%20been%20issued%20on%20August%205%2C%202021%2C%20specifically%20targeting%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20lapses%20in%20disclosures%20between%20April%201%2C%202019%2C%20and%20March%2026%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%20had%20failed%20to%20make%20essential%20disclosures%20to%20stock%20exchanges.%20These%20disclosures%20were%20vital%20in%20assessing%20the%20security%20of%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20debt%20instruments.%20The%20consequences%20of%20these%20lapses%20affected%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20stock%20price%2C%20which%20plummeted%20from%20a%20high%20of%20Rs%2031%20in%20April%202019%20to%20a%20mere%20Rs%200.75%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Price%20Waterhouse%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fpwc-anil-ambani-reliance-capital-home-finance%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20auditor%20of%20Reliance%20Capital%20and%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%20amid%20suspicions%20of%20fraud.%20It%20cited%20an%20inability%20by%20the%20Anil%20Ambani-led%20firms%20to%20satisfactorily%20resolve%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20observations%2Ftransactions%E2%80%9D%20which%20could%20be%20significant%20or%20material%20to%20the%20financial%20statements%20of%20both%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackstory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReliance%20Home%20Finance%20had%20borrowed%20a%20staggering%20sum%20of%20over%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%20from%20banks%20and%20investors%2C%20only%20to%20later%20default%20on%20its%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20violating%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftaxguru.in%2Fsebi%2Fdetailed-analysis-regulation-30-sebi-lodr-regulations-2015.html%5C%22%3ELODR%3C%2Fa%3E%20norms%2C%20or%20Listing%20Obligation%20and%20Disclosure%20Requirements%2C%20which%20say%20that%20a%20listed%20entity%20shall%20disclose%20to%20stock%20exchange(s)%20all%20events%20or%20information%2C%20which%20are%20material%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20reasonably%20possible%20and%20not%20later%20than%2024%20hours%20from%20the%20occurrence%20of%20event%20or%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20SEBI%20regulation%20enables%20transparency%20and%20fair%20disclosures%20by%20all%20listed%20entities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20debt%20resolution%20process%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20lenders%2C%20in%20August%202019%2C%20had%20appointed%20Grant%20Thornton%20to%20conduct%20an%20independent%20forensic%20audit.%20This%20procedure%20is%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20as%20per%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20guidelines%20for%20the%20Prudential%20Framework%20for%20Resolution%20of%20Stressed%20Assets%20in%20cases%20involving%20a%20change%20of%20control%20and%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202020%2C%20the%20auditor%20said%20that%20it%20found%20%E2%80%9Canomalies%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20credit%20appraisal%20process%20of%20the%20company.%20It%20noted%20that%20more%20than%2080%25%20of%20the%20loans%20were%20corporate%20loans%2C%20which%20were%20disbursed%20to%20a%20group%20of%2047%20borrowers%20that%20shared%20these%20common%20characteristics%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Freliance-home-finance-gave-rs-12000-crore-loans-to-indirectly-linked-borrowers-forensic-audit%2Farticleshow%2F73220535.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20people%20aware%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20auditor%20also%20found%20that%20eight%20of%20the%2047%20borrowers%20were%20%E2%80%9Crelated%20parties%E2%80%9D%20of%20Reliance%20Group%20companies%2C%20Reliance%20Power%20and%20Reliance%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%2C%20prior%20to%20disbursal%20of%20loans%20worth%20Rs%201%2C300%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20auditor%20also%20found%20instances%20where%20loans%20granted%20to%20the%20group%20of%2047%20borrowers%20eventually%20found%20their%20way%20back%20to%20Anil%20Ambani%20group%20companies%20through%20onward%20lending%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20people%20quoted%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemorningcontext.com%2Fbusiness%2Fanil-ambani-may-just-go-scot-free%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EMorning%20Context%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20analysis%20published%20on%20September%2020%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20forensic%20audit%20not%20only%20outlined%20the%20movement%20of%20funds%20raised%20from%20investors%20to%20several%20promoter-linked%20companies%2C%20but%20also%20to%20the%20family%20of%20Rana%20Kapoor%2C%20then%20the%20CEO%20of%20Yes%20Bank%2C%20a%20lender%20to%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance.%E2%80%9D%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemorningcontext.com%2Fbusiness%2Fanil-ambani-may-just-go-scot-free%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKapoor%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20March%202020%20in%20connection%20with%20various%20cases%20of%20fraud.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CA%20similar%20transaction%20between%20Kapoor%20and%20Dewan%20Housing%20Finance%20landed%20its%20promoters%2C%20Kapil%20and%20Dhiraj%20Wadhawan%2C%20in%20jail%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fbook-excerpt-the-unravelling-of-anil-ambanis-empire%5C%22%3EBook%20Excerpt%3A%20The%20Unravelling%20of%20Anil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Empire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20lapses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20noted%20how%20Anil%20Ambani%20may%20just%20go%20scot%20free%20and%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthough%20the%20company%20was%20promoted%20by%20Anil%20Ambani%2C%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20show-cause%20notice%20was%20directed%20against%20the%20company%20and%20three%20of%20its%20top%20executives%3A%20chief%20executive%20officer%20Sharad%20Sudhalkar%2C%20company%20secretary%20and%20compliance%20officer%20Parul%20Jain%20and%20chief%20financial%20officer%20Pinkesh%20Shah.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20the%20investigation%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20directly%20with%20Anil%20Ambani%20right%20from%20the%20start%2C%20its%20timing%20and%20rather%20meek%20closure%20with%20a%20small%20fine%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20helping%20him%20slowly%20wriggle%20out%20of%20the%20mess%20caused%20in%20the%20company%20over%20the%20years.%20Of%20course%2C%20lapses%20in%20disclosures%20or%20other%20regulatory%20filings%20are%20in%20general%20treated%20as%20the%20fault%20of%20the%20key%20managerial%20personnel.%20But%20in%20this%20case%2C%20I%20strongly%20believe%20Ambani%20should%20have%20been%20a%20party%20to%20the%20investigation%20as%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20company%20started%20with%20the%20debenture%20funds%20being%20routed%20to%20companies%20related%20to%20the%20promoters%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Morning%20Context%3C%2Fem%3E%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20was%20in%20the%20works%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20its%20final%20order%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Ambani%20is%20no%20longer%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%E2%80%99s%20promoter%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Freliance-home-finance-insolvency-supreme-court-allows-debenture-holders-to-be-covered-under-resolution-plan-of-authum-investments-223316%5C%22%3Ewas%20acquired%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Authum%20Investment%20and%20Infrastructure%2C%20under%20the%20bankruptcy%20resolution%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20case%2C%20SEBI%20had%20not%20conducted%20an%20in-person%20meeting%20with%20the%20company%20officials%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20for%20a%20final%20order%2C%20the%20news%20outlet%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20pr