t%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsecular%26quot%3B%20between%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdemocratic%26quot%3B%20and%20changing%20%26quot%3Bunity%20of%20the%20nation%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bunity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201978%2C%20many%20of%20the%20changes%20were%20reversed%20but%20the%20amended%20preamble%20stayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20%26quot%3Bsecularism%26quot%3B%20is%20part%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%2C%20which%20means%20that%20certain%20basic%20characteristics%20cannot%20be%20erased.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20an%20amendment%20is%20notified%2C%20the%20old%20Constitution%20should%20cease%20to%20be%20printed%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20said.%20Any%20change%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20therefore%2C%20would%20be%20tampering%2C%20they%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695200520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbfas02c_constitution_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farjun-ram-meghwal-adhir-ranjan-chowdhury-preamble-to-constitution-no-socialist-secular-in-constitution-copy-amid-row-law-minister-says-4406089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20absence%20of%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bsocialist%2C%20secular%26quot%3B%20in%20English%20copies%20of%20the%20Constitution%20distributed%20to%20MPs%20yesterday%20has%20provoked%20a%20massive%20controversy%20a%20day%20after%20the%20special%20session%20officially%20moved%20to%20parliament's%20new%20building.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farjun-ram-meghwal-adhir-ranjan-chowdhury-preamble-to-constitution-no-socialist-secular-in-constitution-copy-amid-row-law-minister-says-4406089%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HustleGPT%3A%20Generative%20AI%20will%20boost%20income%20and%20help%2