3A%20%E2%80%9CAll%20parties%20unite%20behind%20India%20but%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20won%E2%80%99t%20slam%20China%3F%E2%80%9D.%20Republic%20TV%E2%80%99s%20main%20debates%20on%20June%2019%20were%20headlined%3A%20%E2%80%9CUnarmed%20with%20fact%2C%20Congress%20insults%20Army%E2%80%9D%3B%20%E2%80%9CIs%20there%20a%20%E2%80%98special%20relation%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20China%3F%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20movement%20against%20China%20gets%20bigger%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20371px)%2085vw%2C%20371px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1-300x208.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22371%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1-300x208.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1-1024x711.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F12100436%2FIMG_0050-1.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-563875%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22257%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPrice%20of%20the%20Modi%20Years%20by%20Aakar%20Patel.%20%3C%2Fem%3EWestland%20(2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20book%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPrice%20of%20the%20Modi%20Years%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20being%20republished%20this%20month%20in%20paperback%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20two%20top%20English%20news%20channels.%20What%20were%20the%20subjects%20of%20their%20prime-time%20debates%20in%20this%20period%20when%20there%20was%20the%20Chinese%20intrusion%20and%20the%20economy%20was%20contracting%20because%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20lockdown%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20of%20May%2C%20June%20and%20July%2C%20Times%20Now%20had%2033%20prime-time%20debates%20which%20criticised%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20It%20had%20none%20that%20criticised%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20There%20were%20zero%20debates%20on%20the%20economic%20recession.%20In%20the%20same%20three%20months%2C%20Republic%20TV%20had%2047%20debates%20that%20criticised%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20It%20had%20none%20that%20criticised%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20none%20on%20the%20economic%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20period%20in%20which%20between%20June%207%20and%20June%2027%2C%20the%20price%20of%20petrol%2Fdiesel%20was%20hiked%20every%20single%20day%20for%2021%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2016%2C%20India%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20lost%2020%20soldiers%2C%20who%20were%20bludgeoned%20to%20death%20in%20hand-to-hand%20combat%20with%20the%20Chinese%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20Ladakh.%20Daily%20Covid%20infections%20rose%20from%202%2C300%20cases%20on%20May%201%20to%20over%2057%2C000%20daily%20cases%20on%20July%2031.%20But%20note%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdebates%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Journalism%20Review%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20another%20note%20that%20the%20PMO%20had%20circulated%20to%20the%20television%20channels%2C%20instructing%20them%20on%20what%20to%20focus%20on.%20The%20note%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20effect%20loud%20and%20clear.%20Taming%20expansionist%20China%20is%20a%20Herculean%20task%20but%20the%20right%20strategies%20and%20actions%20can%20yield%20to%20(sic)%20outstanding%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20pulled%20back.%20China%20has%20been%20pushed%20back%2C%20by%20a%20united%20nation%20led%20by%20a%20leader%20who%20led%20from%20the%20front.%20By%20taking%20decisive%20military%2C%20economic%20and%20strategic%20moves%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20pushed%20back%20China.%20The%20notion%20of%20economic%20infallibility%20of%20China%20has%20received%20a%20tight%20slap%20with%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20clarion%20call%20of%20Atma%20Nirbhar%20Bhar