g%20issues%20that%20impact%20Indians%2C%20such%20as%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20education%20or%20health.%20Instead%2C%20they%20have%20consisted%20mostly%20of%20attacks%20against%20the%20Opposition%20as%20well%20as%20any%20groups%20or%20persons%20that%20oppose%20the%20ruling%20government%E2%80%99s%20ideology.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20figures%20are%20staggering%2C%20if%20unsurprising.%20Nearly%20fifty%20per%20cent%20of%20Republic%20TV%E2%80%99s%20political%20debates%20criticised%20the%20Opposition%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20conducted%20even%20one%20debate%20that%20we%20could%20classify%20as%20being%20in%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20favour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20return%20to%20the%20question%20we%20began%20with%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20the%20evidence%20we%20have%20to%20suggest%20that%20some%20anchors%20and%20TV%20stations%20act%20as%20extensions%20of%20the%20government%3F%20The%20evidence%20is%20quite%20clear%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20seek%20it.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20question%20that%20the%20opposition%20is%20correct%20in%20having%20concluded%20that%20it%20is%20being%20asked%20to%20play%20a%20rigged%20game%20by%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20media.%20It%20has%20every%20right%20to%20refuse%20to%20be%20any%20part%20of%20this.%20One%20hopes%2C%20though%20one%20is%20not%20optimistic%2C%20that%20this%20action%20to%20some%20extent%20corrects%20the%20lunacy%20which%20has%20infected%20our%20national%20media%20and%20has%20damaged%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695200400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-the-india-alliance-is-right-in-boycotting-pro-government-media%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20months%20of%20May%2C%20June%20and%20July%2C%