%2C%20Haynes%20added.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJersey%20Mike's%20proved%20Haynes%20wrong%20during%20my%20recent%20visit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20much%20faster%20and%20more%20efficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeed%20of%20service%3A%20Jersey%20Mike's%20wins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESurprising%20discovery%20%E2%80%93%20Subway%20is%20not%20slicing%20every%20meat%20with%20its%20slicers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subway%20promotes%20deli-sliced%20meats.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20chain%20is%20only%20slicing%20some%20meats.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6508cc9912dc4f001a15fece%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESubway%20promotes%20deli-sliced%20meats.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20chain%20is%20only%20slicing%20some%20meats.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%20rolled%20out%20its%20slicers%20with%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20fanfare%20over%20the%20summer.%20But%2C%20during%20my%20visit%2C%20I%20discovered%20Subway%20is%20not%20slicing%20every%20meat%20served%20on%20the%20subs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20slice%20the%20roast%20beef%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20worker%20told%20me%20as%20she%20prepared%20my%20%2317%20sandwich%2C%20Garlic%20Roast%20Beef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20she%20pointed%20to%20the%20sign%20on%20the%20deli%20window%20that%20notes%20the%20store%20only%20slices%20%26quot%3Bturkey%2C%20ham%2C%20pepperoni%2C%20and%20salami.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20technically%2C%20two%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BDeli%20Heroes%26quot%3B%20sandwiches%20I%20ordered%2C%20Garlic%20Roast%20Beef%20and%20The%20Beast%2C%20are%20not%20made%20with%20all%20deli-sliced%20meats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Subway%2C%20I%20happened%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20store%20that%20wasn't%20slicing%20roast%20beef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rollout%20of%20freshly%20sliced%20meats%20across%20mo