as%20dry%20and%20the%20bread%20was%20like%20chewing%20on%20cardboard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20sandwich%20battle%3A%20Jersey%20Mike's%20versus%20Subway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6508cb7c12dc4f001a15fe48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESubway's%20Turkey%20Titan%2C%20left%2C%20doesn't%20stack%20up%20to%20Jersey%20Mike's%20turkey%20and%20provolone%2C%20according%20to%20Insider's%20Nancy%20Luna.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20one%20bite%20of%20Subway's%20Titan%20Turkey%20sub%20and%20could%20only%20taste%20mayo.%20It%20was%20drenched.%20The%20iceberg%20lettuce%20gave%20the%20sandwich%20a%20nice%20crunch.%20Maybe%20they%20saturated%20it%20in%20mayo%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20super%20dry%20white%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bread%20tastes%20like%20particle%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20eating%20partner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETip%3A%20Luckily%2C%20I%20ordered%20a%20side%20of%20Subway's%20MVP%20Vinaigrette.%20I%20dipped%20the%20sandwich%20in%20the%20dressing%20to%20give%20it%20some%20flavor.%20It%20tasted%20much%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20one%20bite%20of%20Jersey%20Mike's%20turkey%20and%20provolone%20sandwich%2C%20I%20could%20taste%20the%20difference%20in%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bread%20was%20light%2C%20airy%20and%20squishy.%20The%20turkey%20was%20thinly%20sliced%20the%20way%20it%20should%20be%20while%20the%20turkey%20on%20the%20Subway%20sandwich%20looked%20like%20it%20was%20processed%20and%20shipped%20from%20a%20distribution%20supplier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20fault%20with%20the%20Jersey%20Mike's%20sub%20was%20the%20'Mike's%20Way'%20application.%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20any%20of%20the%20red%20wine%20vinegar%20and%20spices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%3A%20%246.59%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJersey%20Mike's%3A%20%249.95%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJersey%20Mike's%20wins%20on%20flavor%20and%20presentation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERoast%20beef%20is%20my%20all-time%20favorite%20meat%20on%20a%20sandwich.%20But%20both%20sandwiches%20were%20disappointing.%20I%20know%20they%20can%20do%20better.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nancy%20Luna%20holds%20up%20roast%20beef%20sandwiches%20from%20Subway%20and%20Jersey%20Mike's.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6508cbf712dc4f001a15fe6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInsider%20food%20reporter%20Nancy%20Luna%20taste%20tested%20roast%20beef%20sandwiches%20from%20Subway%20and%20Jersey%20Mike's.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20excited%20to%20eat%20Subway's%20Garlic%20Roast%20Beef%20sub%20because%20I%20tried%20it%20twice%20this%20summer.%20Both%20times%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20sandwich%20was%20delicious.%20It%20contains%20a%20garlic%20a%C3%AFoli%20sauce%20that%20adds%20flavor%20to%20the%20sandwich%20even%20with%20the%20dry%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sandwich%20I%20ordered%20for%20this%20taste%20test%20was%20terrible.%20I%20could%20barely%20taste%20the%20roast%20beef%20or%20garlic%20sauce.%20The%20inconsistency%20surprised%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20I%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20not%20slicing%20the%20roast%20beef%3F%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20could%20taste%20was%20the%20chewy%20bread%2C%20which%20gummed%20up%20in%20my%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoast%20beef%20and%20provolone%20is%20my%20go-to%20sandwich%20at%20Jersey%20Mike's.%20It%20was%20good%2C%20but%20not%20great.%20This%20sandwich%20contained%20less%20meat%20than%20I've%20received%20in%20the%20past.%20And%2C%20again%2C%20the%20'Mike's%20Way'%20application%20was%20not%20up%20to%20par.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJersey%20Mike's%3A%20%2410.45%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%3A%20%247.09%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20call%20this%20one%20a%20tie