20at%20Subway%20was%20flimsy%20on%20the%20meat.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20a%20worthy%20challenger%20to%20Jersey%20Mike's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nancy%20Luna%20compared%20the%20Grand%20Slam%20Ham%20at%20Subway%20to%20the%20ham%20and%20provolone%20sub%20at%20Jersey%20Mike's.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6508cd39bf943d00195b221e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Subway%20sandwich%2C%20left%2C%20had%20a%20visible%20gap%20in%20the%20middle.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20the%20cross-section%20of%20the%20halved%20six-inch%20Subway%20Grand%20Slam%20Ham%20sub%20and%20immediately%20noticed%20airy%20gaps.%20The%20meat%20was%20not%20tightly%20packed%20compared%20to%20the%20ham%20and%20provolone%20sandwich%20at%20Jersey%20Mike's%2C%20which%20was%20airtight%20and%20stacked%20with%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Subway%20sandwich%2C%20made%20with%20ham%2C%20double%20provolone%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20red%20onions%2C%20and%20mayo%2C%20was%20quite%20delicious.%20I%20could%20taste%20all%20the%20ingredients.%20All%20the%20flavors%20stood%20out.%20The%20bread%20was%20still%20dry%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20drag%20down%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20sandwich%20as%20it%20did%20with%20the%20other%20Subway%20subs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20clearly%20the%20best%20of%20the%20four%20Deli%20Heroes%20sandwiches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20was%20it%20better%20than%20Jersey%20Mike's%20ham%20and%20provolone%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJersey%20Mike's%20ham%20and%20cheese%20sub%20was%20superior.%20But%2C%20again%2C%20the%20Mike's%20Way%20vinegar%20and%20seasoning%20were%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJersey%20Mike's%3A%20%249.25%3Cbr%3ESubway%3A%20%245.99%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%20wins%20because%20the%20value%20is%20much%20better%20for%20nearly%20the%20same%20quality%20sub%20if%20you%20can%20get%20over%20the%20l