%20cannot%20raise%20issues%20concerning%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20said%20Congress%20MPs%20had%20thrashed%20their%20allies%20in%20the%20Well%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20the%20then%20UPA%20government%20had%20brought%20a%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202011.%20He%20then%20mentioned%20the%202012%20discussion%20on%20a%20legislation%20to%20implement%20reservation%20in%20promotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20talk%20about%20the%20Bill%20to%20bring%20reservation%20in%20promotion%2C%20all%20those%20in%20these%20benches%20will%20be%20up%20on%20their%20feet.%20(Congress%20minister)%20V%20Narayanasamy%20was%20presenting%20the%20Bill.%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Yashvir%20Singh%20was%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20MP%3B%20these%20people%20talk%20about%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes.%20Yashvir%20Singh%20had%20snatched%20the%20papers%20from%20Mr%20Narayanasamy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20then%20tried%20to%20grab%20his%20(Yashvir%20Singh)%20collar.%20I%20had%20then%20told%20her%2C%20'you%20are%20not%20the%20dictator%20here%2C%20you%20are%20not%20the%20queen%2C%20you%20cannot%20fight%20here'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dubey%20added.%20%26quot%3BMulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20then%20said%20that%20his%20party's%20MPs%20would%20not%20have%20been%20saved%20if%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20intervene.%20You%20tried%20to%20murder%20MPs.%20Now%20you%20have%20come%20together%20in%20an%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20constitutional%20amendment%20Bill%2C%20tabled%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Tuesday%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20In%202012%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20News%20reports%20from%202012%20describe%20Ms%20Gandhi's%20intervention%20during%20the%20chaos%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20She%20had%20reportedly%20held%20Yashvir%20Singh%20and%20asked%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20are%20you%20doing%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20snatched%20the%20papers%20from%20Mr%20Narayanasamy%2C%20who%20later%20went%20on%20to%20serve%20as%20Puducherry%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20news%20reports%20say%20she%20had%20tried%20to%20take%20the%20papers%20from%20Mr%20Singh's%20hands%2C%20but%20could%20not.%20Late%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20then%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%2C%20had%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Battack%20on%20our%20MPs%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Credits%20Left%20Leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20two%20women%20who%20spoke%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20women%20reservation%20Bill%20the%20most%20were%20Bengal's%20Geeta%20Mukherjee%20and%20BJP's%20Sushma%20Swaraj.%20We%20would%20not%20see%20this%20date%20without%20them.%20But%20Sonia%20ji%20did%20not%20mention%20them.%20What%20kind%20of%20politics%20is%20this%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dubey%20asked.%20Ms%20Mukherjee%20was%20CPI's%20seven-time%20MP%20from%20Bengal's%20Panskura%20between%201980%20and%202000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThrowback%20To%20Sharad%20Yadav's%20%26quot%3BShort%20Hair%26quot%3B%20Remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20Mr%20Dubey%20referred%20to%20a%20remark%20by%20veteran%20politician%20late%20Sharad%20Yadav%20on%20the%20women%20reservation%20Bill%20that%20had%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20The%20women%20reservation%20Bill%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20by%20the%20HD%20Devegowda%20government%20in%201996.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20legislation%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20opposed%20the%20move.%20During%20his%20speech%2C%20he%20had%20remarked%20that%20the%20Bill%20would%20empower%20only%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20with%20short%20hair%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20euphemism%20for%20educated%20and%20modern%20women.%20The%20BJP%20MP's%20remarks%20had%20sparked%20a%20row%2C%20forcing%20him%20to%20eventually%20apologise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1