oritise%20transformation%20of%20the%20mindset.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20they%20demonstrate%20genuine%20respect%20for%20women%20by%20aligning%20their%20actions%20with%20their%20words.%20It%20is%20crucial%20that%20they%20take%20appropriate%20action%20against%20those%20who%20are%20harming%20women%20and%20showing%20them%20disrespect%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20golden%20girls%20of%20the%20country%20who%20got%20us%20medals%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20and%20they%20were%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar.%20But%20the%20perpetrator%20sits%20here%20today%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20brought%20to%20book.%20So%20if%20you%20are%20really%20interested%20in%20taking%20women%20towards%20betterment%20and%20progress%2C%20why%20don't%20you%20take%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MP%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Dastidar%20went%20on%20to%20ask%20why%20no%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20in%20the%20Hathras%20and%20Unnao%20rape-and-murder%20cases.%20%26quot%3BA%20little%20girl%20was%20stoned%20to%20death%20in%20Jammu%20and%20the%20wrestlers%2C%20like%20I%20said%2C%20have%20been%20manhandled%20and%20molested%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESalaries%20Not%20Paid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20wages%20and%20salaries%20of%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20of%20people%2C%20from%20those%20working%20under%20the%20employment%20guarantee%20Act%20to%20those%20employed%20as%20scientists%20and%20researchers%20with%20ISRO%20and%20the%20IITs%20have%20not%20been%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20women%20who%20work%20in%20the%20fields%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%2C%20but%20their%20payment%20has%20not%20been%20released%20yet.%20The%20researchers%20and%20scientific%20workers%20of%20ISRO%20and%20IITs%20are%20also%20being%20denied%20their%20salaries.%20I%20had%20requested%20the%20honourable%20minister%20in%20the%20last%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Dastidar%20alleged%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20women%20researchers%20of%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20are%20not%20getting%20their%20salaries%2C%20not%20getting%20their%20stipends.%20This%20is%20a%20fact.%20In%20ISRO%2C%20the%20women%20scientists%2C%20even%20after%20sending%20Chandrayaan%2C%20are%20not%20being%20paid%20their%20salaries.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20respect%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Catch%20Me%20If%20You%20Can'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supports%20the%20bill%20and%20has%20already%20implemented%20over%2033%25%20'reservation'%20for%20women%2C%20Ms%20Dastidar%20quoted%20legendary%20boxer%20Muhammad%20Ali's%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bcatch%20me%20if%20you%20can%26quot%3B%20to%20say%20that%20other%20parties%20should%20catch%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWest%20Bengal%20is%20the%20only%20state%20in%20the%20country%20which%20has%20a%20female%20chief%20minister.%20The%20BJP%20has%20its%20governments%20in%2016%20states%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20women%20chief%20ministers%20there.%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20had%20said%20it%20is%20the%20awakening%20of%20women%20which%20awakes%20India%20towards%20development.%20Bengal%20has%20the%20most%20number%20of%20women%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20the%20most%20women%20ministers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20right%20from%202014%2C%20we%20have%20been%20having%20more%20than%2033%25%20reservation%20within%20the%20party%2C%20so%20to%20say%2C%20without%20any%20forceful%20reservation%20being%20implemented%20through%20any%20parliamentary%20procedure%20or%20the%20election%20commission.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20women%20members%2C%20and%20also%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20This%20is%20what%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Gimmick'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20asked%20why%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20had%20not%20been%20brought%20in%202014%20and%20why%20it%20was%20being%20tabled%20just%20before%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20it%20not%20brought%20in%202014%3F%20What%20are%20they%20trying%20to%20prove%20to%20the%20people.%20Is%20it%20like%20a%20gimmick%2C%20is%20it%20like%20pulling%20a%20rabbit%20from%20their%20hat%20and%20placing%20it%20before%20the%20country.%20This%20government%20has%20raised%20many%20questions%20against%20themselves%2C%20Why%20is%20the%20delimitation%20linked%20with%20the%20reservation%3F%20It%20is%20a%20sinister%20move%20and%20will%20have%20more%20members%20in%20parliament%20from%20states%20that%20have%20failed%20in%20population%20control%20and%20women's%20empowerment%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Dastidar%20alleged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20is%20called%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695199560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Figjnbrko_kakoli-ghosh-dastidar-650_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-why-didnt-bjp-act-on-mp-who-sexually-abused-wrestlers-trinamool-mp-4406588%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20fiery%20speech%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress'%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20trained%20her%20guns%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20asked%20why%20it%20did%20not%20act%20against%20its%20own%20MP%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20wrestlers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-