%20the%20night%20of%209th%20August%20and%20was%20severely%20abused%20sexually%20too%20%5Bas%20is%20evidently%20found%20him%20being%20paraded%20naked%20amidst%20a%20mob%20of%20seniors%3B%20and%20also%20vehemently%20protesting%20against%20being%20labelled%20a%20gay)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-swapnadeep-kundu%5C%22%3EJU%20First%20Year%20Student%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Ragging%E2%80%99%20Death%20Draws%20Attention%20to%20Systemic%20Flaws%20and%20Discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20noting%20it%20does%20not%20have%20%E2%80%9Cconclusive%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20on%20how%20the%20student%20fell%20from%20the%20top%20floor%2C%20the%20committee%2C%20however%2C%20identified%20two%20possibilities%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20case%20of%20abetted%20incident%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CA%20case%20of%20homicide%E2%80%9D.%20The%20committee%20cautioned%20that%20the%20identified%20possibilities%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20%E2%80%9Cexhaustive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20panel%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20provides%20a%20blow-by-blow%20account%20of%20what%20had%20happened%20before%20the%20student%20fatally%20fell%20from%20his%20hostel%20building%20on%20August%209.%20Around%207%3A30%20pm%20that%20day%2C%20the%20victim%20was%20taken%20to%20Room%20No%3A%2059%20of%20the%20hostel%E2%80%99s%20A-2%20block%20together%20with%20a%20few%20other%20%E2%80%98fresher%E2%80%99%20students%20by%20seniors.%20They%20were%20then%20forced%20to%20shout%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20objectionable%2C%20sexist%2C%20and%20abusive%20lines%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20women%20residents%20of%20Police%20Quarters%20next%20to%20the%20hostel.%20The%20victim%20was%20pressured%20into%20falling%20in%20line%20by%20seniors%20after%20he%20initially%20refused%20to%20utter%20such%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20harassment%20by%20seniors%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20%E2%80%9Cliterally%20shattered%E2%80%9D%20him%20and%20the%20deceased%20student%20broke%20into%20tears%2C%20the%20report%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20seniors%20further%20intimidated%20the%20victim%20by%20stating%20that%20police%20would%20take%20action%20against%20the%20victim%20for%20his%20utterances%20of%20such%20abusive%20words%20towards%20their%20quarters.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20the%20victim%20got%20very%20scared%20and%20started%20crying.%20Almost%20simultaneously%2C%20he%20felt%20a%20sheer%20bout%20of%20stomach%20pain%20and%20sat%20down%20clutching%20his%20abdomen.%20He%20was%20then%20given%20an%20antacid%20tablet%20by%20a%20senior%2C%20and%20then%20singularly%20led%20away%20by%20few%20seniors%20to%20another%20room%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20sweating%20profusely%20due%20to%20mental%20stress%20around%208%3A20%20pm%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20dining%20hall%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20students%20who%20deposed%20before%20the%20committee%2C%20it%20concluded%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20sweating%20profusely%20due%20to%20tremendous%20pressure%20from%20seniors%2C%20and%20that%20they%20were%20drinking%20heavily%20in%20his%20room.%20The%20committee%20also%20recorded%20statements%20of%20other%20students%20in%20the%20same%20hostel%20who%20smelled%20a%20strong%20odour%20of%20alcohol%20emanating%20from%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20taken%20along%20with%20other%20first-year%20students%20on%20the%20same%20night%2C%20between%209%20pm%20and%2010%3A45%20pm%2C%20to%20A-2%20block%20for%20ragging%2C%20he%20was%20soon%20singled%20out%20for%20%E2%80%9Csevere%20ragging%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%2C%20the%20committee%20notes%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20systematic%20and%20planned%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20few%20depositors%20(deponents)%20reported%20that%20they%20heard%20a%20howling%20noise%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block.%20At%20past%2011.30%20pm%2C%20one%20of%20the%20depositors%20(deponents)%20reported%20to%20have%20heard%20a%20loud%20cry%20out%20(for%20help)%20by%20a%20single%20person%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20boarders%2C%20on%20hearing%20the%20loud%20cry%20went%20sprinting%20to%20the%20second-floor%20corridor%20of%20A-2%20block%2C%20and%20reported%20to%20have%20seen%20victim%20running%20in%20a%20completely%20naked%20state%2C%20and%20desperately%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20toilet%20of%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20A-2%20block%2C%20and%20then%20rushing%20into%20room%20no.%2065.%20Even%20as%20the%20victim%20tried%20to%20close%20the%20door%20of%20room%20no.%2065%20from%20inside%2C%20seniors%20pushed%20open%20the%20door%20and%20pulled%20him%20out.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20was%20reportedly%20offered%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%2C%20which%20he%20gulped%20a%20bit%2C%20and%20then%20threw%20the%20bottle%20at%20a%20senior%2C%20all%20the%20while%20standing%20stark%20naked%20in%20front%20of%20many%20seniors%20in%20the%20second-floor%20well-lit%20lobby%2C%20facing%20utter%20humiliation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20victim%20desperately%20ran%20in%20the%20corridor%20of%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20A-2%20block%20naked%20as%20around%2020%20seniors%20and%20alumni%20looked%20at%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20large%20mob%20of%20seniors%20present%20there%20in%20both%20upper%20and%20lower%20staircases%2C%20thereby%20incidentally%20blocking%20any%20escape%20route%20for%20the%20hapless%20victim%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%2C%20however%2C%20underlines%20that%20the%20information%20on%20how%20the%20victim%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%20from%20the%20top%20floor%20is%20%E2%80%9Cuncertain%20and%20vague%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CInformation%20regarding%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20movements%2C%20just%20prior%20to%20his%20fatal%20fall%2C%20and%20eventual%20fall%2C%20is%20rather%20uncertain%20and%20vague%2C%20as%20none%20of%20the%20depositors%20(deponents)%20gave%20a%20clear-cut%20description%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98fall%E2%80%99%20incident%2C%20which%20could%20help%20in%20ascertaining%20the%20cause%20and%20sequence%20of%20the%20mishap.%20Many%20have%20reported%20to%20have%20seen%20the%20victim%20run%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20corridor%20with%20a%20senior%20following%20him%2C%20but%20thereafter%2C%20the%20depositors%20(deponents)%20seem%20to%20have%20lost%20sight%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98final%20fall%E2%80%99%20due%20to%20one%20reason%20or%20the%20other%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20student%20fell%2C%20the%20accused%20cleaned%20the%20blood%20stains%20with%20water%20and%20tried%20to%20suppress%20facts%20and%20remove%20evidence%2C%20the%20committee%20alleged.%20The%20senior%20students%20also%20called%20a%20number%20of%20meetings%20with%20hostellers%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20narrative%20they%20would%20present%20to%20the%20police%20and%20media%2C%20and%20that%20nobody%20would%20present%20any%20other%20version%2C%20the%20committee%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20panel%20also%20said%20that%20hostel%20superintendents%20deposed%20before%20it%20alleging%20a%20number%20of%20instances%20when%20they%20were%20harassed%20by%20seniors%20and%20illegal%20boarders%20in%20the%20hostel.%20No%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20university%20administration%20even%20after%20they%20had%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20students%20who%20harassed%20them%2C%20the%20hostel%20superintendents%20told%20the%20probe%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695199404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12142242%2FScreenshot-2023-08-12-at-2.16.26.png%22%2