0influencer%2C%20I%20have%20every%20right%20to%20speak%20up%20wherever%20I%20want%20to%20and%20whenever%20it%20is%20needed...%20I%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20against%20my%20state%20and%20my%20motherland%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Laishram%2C%20who%20has%20acted%20in%20over%20100%20Manipuri%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20called%20to%20represent%20Manipur%20in%20the%20Northeast%20festival%20as%20a%20show%20stopper%2C%20I%20only%20went%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20supporting%20my%20state%2C%20and%20spreading%20awareness%20(about%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20violence)%20among%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20present%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2031-year-old%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20Laishram%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20the%20public%20and%20film%20associations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20a%20top%20functionary%20of%20the%20Film%20Forum%20Manipur%20asserted%20that%20such%20interference%20is%20unfortunate%20and%20uncalled%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20175%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20several%20hundreds%20injured%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20when%20a%20'Tribal%20Solidarity%20March'%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeiteis%20account%20for%20about%2053%20per%20cent%20of%20Manipur's%20population%20and%20live%20mostly%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%2C%20while%20tribals%2C%20including%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%2C%20constitute%2040%20per%20cent%20and%20reside%20mostly%20in%20the%20hill%20districts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695198960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023