irst%20speaker%20from%20the%20Opposition%20on%20the%20bill%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%20her%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhis-top-quotes-on-womens-reservation-bill-delay-in-implementing-womens-quota-bill-will-4406183%5C%22%3Esupports%20the%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20demanded%20a%20reservation%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20within%20the%2033%25%20quota%20for%20women.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20speaking%20on%20the%20bill%20was%20an%20emotional%20moment%20for%20her%20as%20her%20husband%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20first%20to%20introduce%20a%20bill%20on%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20local%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20Long%20Journey'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Hindi%2C%20the%20former%20Congress%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20I%20stand%20here%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam.%20From%20smoke-filled%20kitchens%20to%20flood-lit%20stadiums%2C%20the%20Indian%20woman's%20journey%20has%20been%20a%20long%20one.%20But%20she%20has%20finally%20reached%20her%20destination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20women%20have%20fought%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20men%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20Independence%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20India%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSpeaking%20on%20this%20bill%20is%20an%20emotional%20moment%20for%20me%20because%20the%20constitutional%20amendment%20providing%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20local%20bodies%20had%20first%20been%20tabled%20by%20my%20husband%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20It%20was%20a%20Congress%20government%20under%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20that%20had%20got%20it%20passed.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20dream%20has%20only%20been%20half%20fulfilled%20so%20far%20and%20it%20will%20be%20fulfilled%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20this%20bill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20while%20her%20party%20supports%20the%20bill%2C%20women%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20wait%20longer%20to%20get%20their%20rights.%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20years%20will%20they%20have%20to%20wait%2C%20two%2C%20four%2C%20eight%3F%20Is%20this%20right%3F%20The%20Congress%20demands%20that%20the%20bill%20be%20implemented%20immediately.%20A%20caste%20census%20must%20also%20be%20conducted%20and%20a%20provision%20must%20be%20made%20for%20reservation%20for%20women%20from%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20communities.%20The%20government%20should%20take%20all%20the%20steps%20needed%20for%20this.%20Delaying%20this%20would%20be%20doing%20gross%20injustice%20to%20women.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Hits%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20bill%20already%20has%20a%20provision%20for%20reservation%20for%20women%20from%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20said%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Opposition%20had%20not%20tabled%20the%20bill%20all%20these%20years%20and%20are%20now%20upset%20because%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20showed%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20been%20saying%20it%20is%20the%20right%20time%2C%20this%20is%20the%20time%20(to%20pass%20the%20bill).%20We%20are%20proud%20of%20him%20for%20calling%20this%20special%20session%20to%20table%20this%20bill%20and%20give%20respect%2C%20and%20reservation%2C%20to%20the%20women%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20country%20runs%20on%20the%20Constitution.%20They%20have%20been%20patting%20themselves%20on%20the%20back%20for%20introducing%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20panchayats%20and%20local%20bodies.%20They%20never%20spoke%20about%2C%20or%20provided%20for%2C%20OBC%20reservation.%20They%20are%20bringing%20up%20new%20things%20for%20political%20angles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20now%20saying%20implement%20the%20reservation%20from%202024%20itself%20(without%20carrying%20out%20the%20Census%20and%20delimitation).%20Do%20you%20want%20the%20reservation%20to%20be%20struck%20down%3F%20Do%20you%20want%20us%20to%20use%20women's%20reservation%20as%20a%20lollipop%2C%20like%20you%20did%3F%20The%20PM%20says%20he%20finishes%20what%20he%20starts.%20And%20now%20that%20the%20bill%20has%20been%20tabled%2C%20women%20will%20get%20their%20rights%2C%20and%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20across%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20cleared%20by%20both%20Houses%20with%20the%20support%20of%20some%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20including%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695198480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fe0499ta8_sonia-gandhi-new-parliament-1200_650x400_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fobcs-should-be-included-in-womens-reservation-bill-sonia-gandhi-in-parliament-4406114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20first%20speaker%20from%20the%20Opposition%20on%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20former%20Congress%20President%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%20her%20party%20supports%20the%20legislation%2C%20but%20demanded%20a%20reservation%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fobcs-should-be-included-in-womens-reservation-bill-sonia-gandhi-in-parliament-4406114%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fobcs-should-be-included-in-womens-reservation-bill-sonia-gandhi-in-parliament-4406114%2Famp%2F