%20there%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20free%20speech%20is%20protected%2C%20the%20same%20would%20be%20illegal%20when%20it%20%26quot%3Bcrosses%20the%20line%26quot%3B%20and%20results%20in%20tarnishing%20and%20jeopardising%20individual%20personality%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20the%20plaintiff's%20name%2C%20voice%2C%20dialogue%2C%20image%20in%20illegal%20manner%2C%20that%20too%20for%20commercial%20purposes%2C%20cannot%20be%20permitted.%20Court%20cannot%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20such%20misuse%20of%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefendants%201%20to%2016%20are%20restrained%20from%20using%20...%20in%20any%20manner%20the%20plaintiff%20Anil%20Kapoor's%20name%2C%20likeness%2C%20voice%20or%20any%20other%20attributes%20of%20his%20personality%20...%20for%20monetary%20gain%20or%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20restrained%20other%20unknown%20persons%20from%20disseminating%20the%20offending%20links.%20The%20court%20directed%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20block%20the%20offending%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20%26quot%3Bfame%20for%20a%20person%20comes%20with%20disadvantages%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthis%20case%20shows%20that%20reputation%20and%20fame%20can%20transcend%20into%20damage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20misuse%20can%20damage%20a%20celebrity's%20right%20to%20endorsement%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695196560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fg3qnqbeo_anil-kapoor_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdelhi-hc-restrains-misuse-of-personality-attributes-of-actor-anil-kapoor-4406308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Advocate%20Pravin%20Anand%20said%20several%20websites%20and%20platforms%20have%20been%20misusing%20the%20personality%20rights%20of%20Anil%20Kapoor%20through%20various%20activities%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdelhi-hc-restrains-misuse-of-personality-attributes-of-actor-anil-kapoor-4406308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdelhi-hc-restrains-misuse-of-personality-attributes-of-actor-anil-kapoor-4406308%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdelhi-hc-restrains-misuse-of-personality-attributes-of-actor-anil-kapoor-4406308%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20Does%20Not%20Need%20Ratification%20By%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20will%20not%20need%20a%20sign-off%20by%20states%20if%20it%20is%20passed%20in%20parliament%20with%20a%20special%20majority.%20Under%20Article%20368%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20a%20special%20majority%20requires%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20members%20present%20and%20voting%20to%20support%20a%20bill%2C%20as%20well%20as%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20total%20members%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%2C%20seeks%20the%20reservation%20of%2033%25%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20some%20reports%20claimed%20that%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20368%2C%20the%20Constitution%20amendment%20bill%20will%20require%20ratification%20by%20at%20least%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20women's%20quota%20bill%20has%20been%20brought%20under%20a%20rule%20that%20requires%20a%20special%20majority%20but%20no%20ratification%20by%20states.%20That%20is%20because%20according%20to%20the%20government%2C%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20does%20not%20affect%20the%20representation%20of%20states%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20approval%20by%20states%20would%20be%20needed%20for%20subjects%20like%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20or%20High%20Court%20or%20Centre-State%20relations.%20The%20last%20bill%20to%20become%20law%20after%20being%20cleared%20by%20parliament%20and%20half%20the%20states%20of%20the%20country%20was%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20Bill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UPA%20government%20led%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%20introduced%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202008%2C%20where%20it%20was%20passed%20in%202010.%20However%2C%20the%20Bill%20never%20reached%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20consideration.%20The%20Bill%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20key%20campaign%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20both%20the%202014%20and%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20promises%20a%2033%25%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20Parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%2C%20but%20this%20may%20not%20come%20into%20effect%20until%202029%2C%20NDTV%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women's%20quota%20can%20only%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20first%20delimitation%2C%20or%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%2C%20following%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20place%20in%202027%2C%20as%20delimitation%20is%20only%20conducted%20after%20the%20next%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695196260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fovml5cm8_new-parliament_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-special-session-womens-reservation-bill-does-not-need-ratification-by-states-4406412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%