20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20family%20members%20were%20sent%20for%20medical%20treatment%20to%20neighbouring%20Bareilly%20district%20where%20Alok%20Gupta%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries.%20The%20other%20family%20members%20are%20still%20receiving%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20caused%20huge%20anger%20among%20locals%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20trading%20community%20who%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20Gupta%20residence%20in%20large%20numbers%20and%20demanded%20action%20from%20the%20police.%20The%20local%20traders%E2%80%99%20union%20threatened%20to%20shut%20all%20the%20shops%20in%20the%20kasba.%20The%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Bareilly%2C%20Rakesh%20Singh%2C%20too%20reached%20the%20site%20of%20the%20crime%20and%20promised%20the%20strictest%20action%20against%20those%20who%20committed%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESP%20Meena%20said%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20two%20named%20accused%20and%20other%20unknown%20persons%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20Gupta%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22US%20Law%20Firm%20Seeks%20Action%20Against%20Adityanath%2C%20UP%20Top%20Cops%20for%20%E2%80%98Encounter%E2%80%99%20Killings%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fus-law-firm-seeks-action-against-adityanath-up-top-cops-for-encounter-killings%5C%22%3EUS%20Law%20Firm%20Seeks%20Action%20Against%20Adityanath%2C%20UP%20Top%20Cops%20for%20%E2%80%98Encounter%E2%80%99%20Killings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20police%20said%20they%20arrested%20one%20suspect%20Shahbaz%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20mohalla%20sarai%20in%20Katra.%20The%20murder%20weapon%20was%20also%20recovered%20on%20his%20cue%2C%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShahbaz%20was%20being%20escorted%20to%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20after%20medical%20examination%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20when%20%E2%80%9Csome%20%3Cem%3Epashu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(stray%20animal)%20came%20in%20front%20of%20the%20police%20jeep%20on%20a%20highway%20near%20Batlaiya%20village%20causing%20it%20to%20lose%20balance%2C%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20jeep%20became%20disbalanced%20and%20came%20to%20a%20halt.%20Making%20use%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20he%20snatched%20a%20pistol%20from%20the%20police%20inspector%20and%20jumped%20out%20%5Bof%20the%20vehicle%5D.%20He%20ran%20into%20the%20fields%20and%20started%20firing%20at%20the%20police%20from%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20reinforcements%20were%20called%20in%20and%20repeated%20warnings%20were%20issued%20to%20Shahbaz%20asking%20him%20to%20surrender%20but%20he%20continued%20to%20fire%20at%20the%20police%2C%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20fired%20back%20in%20self-defence%20and%20retaliation%2C%20in%20which%20Shahbaz%20got%20injured%2C%20said%20the%20SP.%20Shahbaz%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20community%20health%20centre%20where%20doctors%20declared%20him%20brought%20dead%2C%20said%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20team%2C%20which%20was%20led%20by%20a%20circle%20officer%2C%20that%20carried%20out%20this%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esarahaniya%20karya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(commendable%20work)%20would%20receive%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20from%20the%20district%20police%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20from%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2010%2C%202020%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20near%20a%20temple%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20Vikas%20Dubey%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20the%20police%20while%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20flee%20from%20custody%20after%20an%20accident%20as%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20from%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20city%20to%20Kanpur.%20This%20was%20days%20after%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20men%20gunned%20down%20eight%20policemen%2C%20including%20a%20deputy%20SP-rank%20officer%2C%20and%20left%20seven%20others%20injured%20when%20a%20police%20team%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20village%20to%20conduct%20a%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Encouraging%20Police%20'Encounters'%20Will%20Lead%20to%20Arbitrary%20State%20Action%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhyderabad-encounter-arbitrary-state-action-justice-chelameswar-summary-justice%5C%22%3EEncouraging%20Police%20%E2%80%98Encounters%E2%80%99%20Will%20Lead%20to%20Arbitrary%20State%20Action%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20shot%20Dubey%20after%20he%20allegedly%20fired%20at%20them%20with%20a%20pistol%20he%20had%20snatched%20from%20a%20police%20officer%20who%20was%20injured%20when%20the%20vehicle%20carrying%20them%20%E2%80%9Coverturned%E2%80%9D.%20The%20UP%20Special%20Task%20Force%20had%20then%20said%20that%20the%20vehicle%20carrying%20Dubey%20lost%20control%20and%20overturned%20when%20the%20driver%2C%20who%20was%20tired%20after%20a%20long%20journey%2C%20turned%20sharply%20to%20avoid%20a%20herd%20of%20cattle%20that%20suddenly%20ran%20on%20to%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDubey%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20accident%20and%20tried%20to%20flee%20towards%20a%20kutcha%20road%20after%20snatching%20a%20pistol%20from%20an%20injured%20policeman%2C%20police%20had%20said.%20Dubey%20was%20surrounded%20from%20all%20four%20sides%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20surrender%20but%20he%20fired%20at%20the%20police%20which%20fired%20back%20in%20self-defence%2C%20the%20UP%20police%20had%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20version%20was%20questioned%20by%20several%20quarters%20and%20the%20controversial%20killing%20was%20termed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20phrase%20popularly%20used%20to%20describe%20extra-judicial%20staged%20executions%20by%20police.%20The%20matter%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%E2%80%9D%20killings%20of%20Dubey%20and%20his%20aides%20even%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state