agency%20had%20also%20said%20that%20if%20they%20do%20not%20wake%20up%20on%20September%2022%2C%20then%20they%20%26quot%3Bwill%20forever%20stay%20there%20as%20India's%20lunar%20ambassador.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Rover%20completed%20its%20assignments.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20It%20is%20now%20safely%20parked%20and%20set%20into%20Sleep%20mode.%3Cbr%3E%20APXS%20and%20LIBS%20payloads%20are%20turned%20off.%3Cbr%3E%20Data%20from%20these%20payloads%20is%20transmitted%20to%20the%20Earth%20via%20the%20Lander.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Currently%2C%20the%20battery%20is%20fully%20charged.%3Cbr%3E%20The%20solar%20panel%20is%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1698010732128764164%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISRO%20had%20said%20that%20Vikram%20lander%20had%20%26quot%3Bexceeded%20mission%20objectives%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20hop%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stated%20objectives%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-scientist-lists-key-achievements-of-isros-chandrayaan-3-mission-4382047%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India's%20third%20lunar%20mission%2C%20were%20a%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%2C%20rover%20roving%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface%2C%20and%20in-situ%20scientific%20experiments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fso-exciting-to-watch-youtube-chief-congratulates-isro-for-over-8-million-views-of-chandrayaan-3-landing-4389330%5C%22%3EYouTube%20Chief%20Congratulates%20ISRO%20For%20Over%208%20Million%20Views%20Of%20Chandrayaan-3%20Landing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Vikram%20lander%20has%20been%20si