726675%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20World%20Cup%202023%20Official%20Anthem%20Out.%20Features%20Ranveer%2C%20Dhanashree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20unveiled%20the%20official%20anthem%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%2020).%20Titled%20'%3Cem%3EDil%20Jashn%20Bole%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20the%20anthem%20features%20Bollywood%20actor%20Ranveer%20Singh%20as%20well%20as%20the%20wife%20of%20Indian%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1394-yuzvendra-chahal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dhanashree%20Verma.%20The%20music%20was%20given%20by%20Pritam%20while%20the%20lyrics%20are%20from%20Shloke%20Lal%2C%20Saaveri%20Verma.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20Anthem%20launch%2C%20superstar%20Ranveer%20Singh%20said%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Star%20Sports%20family%20and%20a%20die-hard%20cricket%20fan%2C%20being%20part%20of%20this%20anthem%20launch%20for%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20is%20truly%20an%20honor.%20It's%20a%20celebration%20of%20the%20sport%20we%20all%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMusician%20Pritam%20also%20shared%20his%20experience%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BCricket%20is%20India's%20greatest%20passion%20and%20composing%20'Dil%20Jashn%20Bole'%20for%20the%20biggest%20World%20Cup%20ever%2C%20has%20been%20a%20tremendous%20honour%20for%20me.%20This%20song%20is%20not%20just%20for%201.4%20billion%20Indian%20fans%20but%20for%20the%20whole%20world%20to%20come%20to%20India%20and%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20biggest%20celebration%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDIL%20JASHN%20BOLE!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCWC23%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23CWC23%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Official%20Anthem%20arriving%20now%20on%20platform%202023%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Board%20the%20One%20Day%20Xpress%20and%20join%20the%20greatest%20cricket%20Jashn%20ever!%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Credits%3A%3Cbr%3E%20Music%20-%20Pritam%3Cbr%3E%20Lyrics%20-%20Shloke%20Lal%2C%20Saaveri%20Verma%3Cbr%3E%20Singers%20-%20Pritam%2C%20Nakash%20Aziz%2C%20Sreerama%20Chandra%2C%20Amit%20Mishra%2C%20Jonita%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F09AK5B8STG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F09AK5B8STG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ICC%20(%40ICC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICC%2Fstatus%2F1704384709646864506%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20video%20encapsulates%20the%20emotions%20of%20the%20global%20fan%20community%2C%20uniting%20nations%20and%20fans%20across%20different%20cultures.%20The%20fan-centric%20anthem%20represents%20an%20epic%20celebration%2C%20designed%20to%20resonate%20with%20hearts%20and%20ignite%20spirits.%20The%20anthem%20embodies%20the%20World%20Cup%20combining%20the%20unique%20Indian%20passion%20for%20cricket%20with%20the%20national%20pride%20of%20all%20competing%20nations%20to%20create%20an%20unrivalled%20global%20sporting%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFans%20worldwide%20are%20also%20invited%20to%20take%20part%20by%20showcasing%20their%20creative%20interpretations%20of%20the%20hook-step%20in%20diverse%20global%20locations.%20Whether%20it's%20cricket%20stadiums%2C%20educational%20institutions%2C%20iconic%20landmarks%2C%20or%20historical%20monuments%2C%20the%20stage%20is%20theirs.%20Fans%20need%20to%20simply%20team%20up%20with%20a%20friend%2C%20capture%20their%20unique%20hook-step%20performance%2C%20and%20share%20it%20on%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram%20with%20the%20hashtag%20%23CWC23.%20The%20most%20captivating%20videos%20will%20be%20curated%20to%20craft%20a%20collective%20Fan%20Anthem%2C%20showcasing%20the%20world's%20enthusiasm%20for%20all%20to%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClaire%20Furlong%2C%20the%C2%A0ICC%20General%20Manager%20for%20Marketing%20and%20Communications%2C%20said%20on%20the%20occasion%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20ever%20with%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20fans%20around%20the%20world%20ready%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%20The%20anthem%20brilliantly%20captures%20the%20passion%20and%20energy%20of%20India%20and%20the%20fans%20that%20will%20make%20this%20event%20so%20special%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20wait%20for%20the%20world%20to%20hear%20it.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20World%20Cup%20will%20put%20place%20fans%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20action%20and%20the%20anthem%20will%20help%20bring%20them%20closer%20to%20the%20game%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20so%20go%20listen%20now%20and%20create%20your%20own%20hook-step.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%20Star%20Sports%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20delighted%20to%20collaborate%20with%20the%20ICC%20for%20the%20official%20anthem%20of%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20anthem%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20cornucopia%20of%20emotions%20and%20waves%20of%20energy%2C%20which%20each%20and%20every%20day%20of%20the%20tournament%20promises%20to%20deliver%20to%20more%20than%20a%20billion%20viewers%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20gets%20underway%20from%20October%205%2C%20with%20the%20final%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2019th.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695193200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F50jktsj_icc-anthem_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Ficc-world-cup-2023-official-anthem-dil-jashn-bole-out-features-ranveer-singh-dhanashree-verma-4406256%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ICC%20launched%20the%20official%20anthem%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20