aths%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%202040%20if%20nearly%20half%20of%20those%20in%20the%2030-79%20age%20group%20with%20hypertension%20are%20able%20to%20control%20their%20blood%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20released%20during%20the%2078th%20Session%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Fncds%2Fncd-surveillance%2Fhypertension-profiles-2023.pdf%5C%22%3E'Global%20report%20on%20hypertension%3A%20The%20race%20against%20a%20silent%20killer'%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20that%20188.3%20million%20people%20in%20the%20same%20age%20group%20are%20suffering%20from%20hypertension.%20It%20added%20that%20only%2037%20per%20cent%20of%20Indians%20are%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20condition%20in%20time%2C%20and%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20them%20get%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20achieve%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20control%20rate%2C%2067%20million%20more%20people%20with%20hypertension%20would%20need%20to%20be%20effectively%20treated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fcovid-19-linked-with-an-increased-risk-of-hypertension-finds-study-4317960%5C%22%3ECovid-19%20Linked%20With%20An%20Increased%20Risk%20Of%20Hypertension%2C%20Finds%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20report%20is%20based%20on%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20data%20where%20blood%20pressure%20is%20140%2F90%20mmHg%20or%20higher%20or%20a%20person%20is%20taking%20medication%20for%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHypertension%20leads%20to%20stroke%2C%20heart%20attacks%2C%20heart%20failure%2C%20kidney%20damage%20and%20numerous%20other%20health%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20a%20healthy%20diet%2C%20engaging%20in%20regular%20physical%20activity%2C%20managing%20stress%20levels%2C%20and%20regular%20monitoring%20of%20blood%20pressure%20are%20key%20components%20of%20preventing%20hypertension.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695191460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F7ghiv7r8_hypertension_625x300_17_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-hypertension-report-says-4-6-million-lives-can-be-saved-in-india-if-4406197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20titled%20'Global%20report%20on%20hypertension%3A%20The%20race%20against%20a%20silent%20killer'%20said%20that%20188.3%20million%20people%20in%20India%20are%20suffering%20from%20hypertension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-hypertension-report-says-4-6-million-lives-can-be-saved-in-india-if-4406197%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-hypertension-report-says-4-6-million-lives-can-be-saved-in-india-if-4406197%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-hypertension-report-says-4-6-million-lives-can-be-saved-in-india-if-4406197%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akasa%20Air%20gets%20nod%20for%20international%20flights%3B%20eyes%20these%20destinations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695191257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-103801420%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-3966%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fakasa-air-gets-nod-for-international-flights-eyes-middle-eastern-destinations%2Farticleshow%2F103801362.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20development%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20for%20Akasa%20Air%2C%20allowing%20the%20carrier%20to%20expand%20its%20horizons%20into%20potentially%20more%20profitable%20international%20routes%20which%20offer%20less%20competition.%22%2C%22author%