%20the%20government%20itself%20has%20said%20that%20there%20this%20no%20way%20the%20reservations%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Bill%20can%20become%20a%20reality%20before%20the%202029%20general%20elections%2C%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Why%3F%20Because%20India%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20had%20a%20Census%20since%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20next%20delimitation%20exercise%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20exercise%20is%20predicated%20on%20updated%20Census%20numbers.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20next%20Census%20will%20only%20be%20conducted%20sometime%20after%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20scheduled%20for%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20sent%20to%20all%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20in%20June%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20(RGI)%2C%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20the%20Census%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcensus-delayed-deadline-administrative-boundaries-pushed-8697397%2F%5C%22%3Eextended%20the%20deadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20freezing%20administrative%20boundaries%20to%20January%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20general%20elections%20only%20a%20few%20months%20away%2C%20the%20exercise%20is%20not%20possible%20in%202023%20as%20the%20entire%20government%20machinery%20will%20be%20busy%20preparing%20and%20holding%20elections%20across%20states%20and%20UTs.%20A%20census%20enumeration%20can%20only%20start%20a%20few%20months%20after%20administrative%20boundaries%20are%20established.%20Also%2C%20a%20house-listing%20enumeration%20will%20take%20place%20prior%20to%20the%20census%20to%20conduct%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%20(NPR)%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20government%20official%20working%20with%20the%20RGI%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fwomen-reservation-bill-once-again-puts-spotlight-on-much-delayed-census-2021%2Farticleshow%2F103791621.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NPR%2C%20which%20the%20government%20likely%20has%20plans%20to%20integrate%20with%20the%20upcoming%20Census%2C%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue.%20Critics%20believe%20that%20alongside%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(for%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fhome-ministry-seeks-eighth-extension-to-frame-caa-rules%2Farticle67169456.ece%5C%22%3Eyet%20to%20frame%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20passing%20the%20Act%20four%20years%20ago)%2C%20the%20NPR%20may%20be%20used%20to%20deny%20Indian%20Muslims%20of%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20government%20claimed%20that%20the%20Census%20was%20delayed%20because%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20years%20since%2C%20all%20activities%20have%20resumed%20to%20full%20capacity%20and%20multiple%20state%20elections%20have%20been%20held.%20The%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20has%20not%20announced%20why%20it%20has%20not%20conducted%20the%20Census%20despite%20the%20pandemic%20no%20longer%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20any%20administrative%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20time%20since%20the%20last%20Census%20was%20conducted%2C%20India%20has%20overtaken%20China%20to%20become%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Findia-china-highest-populated%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20UN%20projections%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20since%20the%20country%20has%20not%20enumerated%20its%20own%20population%2C%20government%20data%20cannot%20confirm%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20when%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20announced%20the%20Budget%2C%20observers%20noticed%20that%20the%20allocation%20for%20census-related%20activities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-2023-rs-1-564-crore-allocated-for-census-2021-101675243599156.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520is%2520part%2520of%2520the%2Cin%2520the%2520Parliament%2520on%2520Wednesday.%5C%22%3Ehad%20been%20cut%20drastically%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20allocation%20the%20year%20before.%20Budget%202022-23%20had%20put%20aside%20Rs%203%2C676%20crore%20for%20such%20activities%2C%20while%20Budget%202023-24%20put%20aside%20Rs%201%2C564%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20revised%20estimate%20for%202022-23%20was%20even%20lower%20than%20the%20allocation%20for%202023-24%3A%20Rs%20552.65%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20delayed%20Census%20exercise%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20implications%20this%20has%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20%E2%80%93%20has%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Renowned%20economic%20Pronab%20Sen%2C%20who%20has%20been%20named%20as%20head%20of%20the%20government%20panel%20set%20up%20to%20review%20statistical%20surveys%20and%20suggest%20improvements%2C%20says%20all%20data%20generated%20by%20the%20government%20%E2%80%93%20on%20jobs%2C%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20is%20effected%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20Census%20numbers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20quality%20of%20any%20statistical%20survey%20depends%20on%20census%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdelay-in-indias-census-hurting-quality-of-survey-reports-says-official%2Farticleshow%2F101942861.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20has%20also%20led%20to%20speculation%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20motivations.%20For%20instance%2C%20an%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fwhy-is-the-government-delaying-census-2021%2Farticle66413377.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20noted%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20delay%20could%20be%20tactical.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20enumerating%20the%20population%20sizes%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20and%20wants%20to%20hold%20back%20until%20the%20general%20elections%20are%20over.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESecond%2C%20the%20findings%20might%20not%20confirm%20the%20hysteria%20about%20growth%20rates%20of%20certain%20religious%20groups%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20standard%20campaigning%20trope%20for%20leaders%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20every%20election.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThird%2C%20the%20data%20on%20fertility%20rates%20of%20religious%20groups%20might%20also%20present%20certain%20inconvenient%20truths.%20Four%2C%20the%20claims%20of%20achievements%20in%20human%20development%20and%20access%20to%20amenities%20might%20also%20be%20belied%20by%20census%20data.%20Whatever%20the%20reason%2C%20the%20government%20has%20offered%20no%20credible%20explanation%20for%20delaying%20Census%202021.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695190703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20114719%2Findia-1723464_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findias-delayed-census-in-the-spotlight-again-as-womens-reservation-will-have-to-wait%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20women's%20reservation%20Bill%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20next%20delimitation%20exercise%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20exercise%20is%20predicated%20on%20updated%20Census%20numbers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findias-delayed-census-in-the-spotlight-again-as-womens-reservation-will-have-to-wait%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yamuna%2C%20Noida%20Expressways%20To%20Be%20Out%20Of%20Bounds%20For%205%20Days.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20