owards%20the%20state%20FLN%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%20analyses%20that%20non-inclusive%20pedagogy%2C%20non-conceptual%20FLN%20frameworks%2C%20and%20low%20teacher%20capacities%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20why%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20vulnerable%20children%20are%20not%20learning%20as%20they%20should.%20Sonali%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20look%20at%20%5Bhigh-income%5D%20countries%2C%20their%20solutions%20were%20very%20high%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20assistive%20technology%2C%20accessible%20content%E2%80%A6that%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20in%20a%20country%20like%20ours%2C%20which%20has%20low%20digital%20penetration.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20teacher%20ratio%20and%20the%20special%20educator%20ratios%20are%20abysmal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20Government%20data%20suggests%20that%20the%20teacher%20ratio%20has%20fallen%20from%2043%20in%202010-11%20to%2026.3%20in%202020-%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%2C%20she%20says%2C%20focuses%20more%20on%20education%20outcomes%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20subsequently%20increase%20livelihood%20opportunities.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20a%20lifespan%20approach%20because%20only%20working%20on%20education%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient.%20Even%20when%20we%20complete%20education%2C%20if%20the%20children%20are%20still%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%20then%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20point.%20So%20to%20improve%20life%20outcomes%2C%20we%20include%20that%20under%20our%20focus%20for%20age%20groups%20from%205-39.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation's%20UDL%20approach%20emphasises%20flexible%20learning%20environments%20that%20accommodate%20individual%20learning%20differences.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBeneficiary-survey-Gujarat_11zon-1695189667-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330354%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20UDL%20approach%20emphasises%20flexible%20learning%20environments%20that%20accommodate%20individual%20learning%20differences.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMultiple%20children%2C%20multiple%20ways%20to%20learn%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Project%20Ankur%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20Universal%20Design%20for%20Learning%20(UDL)%20approach%20to%20teaching%20and%20learning%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cgives%20all%20students%20equal%20opportunities%20to%20succeed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUDL%20is%20a%20framework%20that%20emphasises%20flexible%20learning%20environments%20that%20accommodate%20individual%20learning%20differences.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20basically%20says%20%E2%80%98Teach%20in%20multiple%20ways%2C%20allow%20the%20child%20to%20respond%20in%20multiple%20ways%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6the%20teaching-learning%20material%20should%20have%20multiple%20modalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonali.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20aims%20to%20bring%20flexibility%20in%20these%20arenas%20so%20they%20can%20be%20adjusted%20as%20per%20an%20individual%20learner%E2%80%99s%20strengths%20and%20needs.%20They%20say%20this%20is%20a%20low-tech%2C%20low-cost%20approach%20that%20is%20suitable%20for%20low-resource%20classrooms%20in%20India.%20The%20resources%20to%20teach%20include%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20adaptable%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20to%20teach%20subtraction%2C%20a%20teacher%20may%20use%20blocks%2C%20number%20lines%2C%20adapted%20worksheets%2C%20and%20flash%20cards.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20you%E2%80%99ve%20exposed%20the%20child%20to%20all%20learning%20methods%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20the%20child%20which%20way%20they%20want%20to%20carry%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonali%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20also%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F234203%2Fnew-national-education-policy-2020-pdf-report-cards-marks-grades-score-cce-continuous-evaluation-descriptive-indicators-sai87%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20ways%20of%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20way%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20allowing%20different%20children%20with%20different%20abilities%20to%20answer%20the%20same%20question%20in%20their%20own%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20a%20child%20is%20non-verbal%2C%20the%20schools%20are%20not%20relying%20on%20oral%20examinations%20alone.%20Instead%2C%20the%20child%20can%20respond%20by%20pointing%20at%20the%20right%20answer%20or%20writing%20it%20down.%20If%20the%20child%20has%20challenges%20in%20reading%2C%20then%20the%20child%20may%20receive%20assistance%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20reader.%20%E2%80%9CInstructions%20are%20broken%20down%2C%20turned%20into%20visuals%E2%80%A6then%20all%20children%20benefit%20with%20these%20interventions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20also%20addressed%20the%20challenge%20of%20multi-grade%20classrooms%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304738%2Fnational-curriculum-framework-for-foundational-stage-education-children-india-ekstep%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreaking%20the%20curriculum%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20types%20of%20learning%20environments%20can%20be%20challenging%20owing%20to%20monograde%20teaching%20material%2C%20low%20availability%20of%20teachers%2C%20rigid%20timetables%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20estimates%20that%20approximately%2078%25%20of%20primary%20schools%20in%20India%20have%20three%20or%20fewer%20teachers%20for%20all%20grade%20levels.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20made%20multi-grade%20plans%2C%20wherein%20we%20say%20here%20are%20your%20common%20activities%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20you%20will%20do%20separately%2C%20and%20that%20way%20we%20address%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20teachers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20EkStep%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695190027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FFunder-visit-Tamil-nadu--1695189484.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330342%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sonali%20Saini%20and%20her%20organisation%20Sol%E2%80%99s%20ARC%20have%20worked%20with%20the%20governments%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20implement%20several%20scalable%2C%20low-cost%2C%20and%20replicable%20policies%20for%20inclusive%20education.%20She%20explains%20why%20these%20could%20be%20key%20in%20transforming%20the%20early%20childhood%20care%20ecosystem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Divya%20Sethu%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330342%2Ftamil-nadu-madhya-pradesh-policies-for-inclusive-education-improve-early-childhood-care-sonali-saini-sols-arc%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stand%20in%20support%20of%20women's%20quota%20bill%2C%20Sonia%20says%3A%20Key%20points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695189777000%2C%22visual%