research%20ships%E2%80%9D%20are%20said%20to%20usually%20have%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20purposes%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20primary%20aim%20is%20scientific%20exploration%2C%20what%20raises%20the%20hackles%20of%20other%20countries%20is%20the%20geopolitical%20purposes%20for%20which%20they%20are%20also%20deployed.%20On%20%3Cem%3EShi%20Yan%206%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cgtn.com%2Fnews%2F2023-09-11%2FChina-s-Shiyan-6-research-ship-sails-for-expedition-in-Indian-Ocean-1n0zYHpBtNC%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%20published%20by%20the%20Chinese%20state%20broadcaster%20CGTN%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20ship%20would%20help%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20scientific%20research%20cooperation%20and%20exchanges%20with%20countries%20along%20the%20Maritime%20Silk%20Road%20and%20further%20realise%20the%20integration%20of%20science%20and%20education%20for%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsfirst.lk%2F2023%2F9%2F18%2Fchina-s-shi-yan-6-heading-to-sri-lanka-pending-clearance%5C%22%3ESri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENewsFirst%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%20international%20maritime%20tracking%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20demonstrating%20that%20the%20Chinese%20geophysical%20scientific%20research%20vessel%20%3Cem%3EShi%20Yan%206%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20has%20also%20attracted%20India%E2%80%99s%20attention%2C%20will%20reach%20the%20port%20of%20Colombo%20on%20September%2029.%20Last%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaderana.lk%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D92959%5C%22%3Eanother%20Sri%20Lankan%20news%20portal%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20had%20%E2%80%9Cgranted%20approval%20for%20the%20Chinese%20geophysical%20and%20seismic%20survey%20vessel%20%E2%80%98Shi%20Yan%206%E2%80%99%20to%20carry%20out%20research%20on%20Sri%20Lankan%20waters%20with%20the%20National%20Aquatic%20Resources%20Research%20and%20Development%20Agency%20(NARA).%E2%80%9D%20A%20Spokesman%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20approval%20was%20granted%20on%20request%20by%20NARA%20and%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnavbharattimes.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fasian-countries%2Fsri-lanka-clears-docking-of-chinese-research-ship-shi-yan-6-at-colombo-india-us-raised-security-concerns%2Farticleshow%2F103778141.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENavbharat%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20a%20report%20datelined%20Colombo%2C%20writes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdeceived%20India%2C%20%3Cem%3E(Bharat%20ko%20diya%20dhok%3C%2Fem%3Ea%3Cem%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ship%2C%20the%20second%20after%20a%20year%2C%20has%20caused%20consternation%20in%20India%2C%20and%20there%20were%20reports%20in%20August%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20was%20processing%20a%20request%20by%20China%20to%20allow%20a%20research%20ship%20to%20dock%20in%20the%20country%2C%20a%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20August%2023%2C%20a%20year%20after%20a%20visit%20by%20a%20Chinese%20spy%20vessel%20to%20the%20Island%20nation%20raised%20security%20concerns%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chinese%20embassy%20here%20has%20made%20an%20application%20and%20the%20ministry%20is%20currently%20looking%20at%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priyanga%20Wickramasingha%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsri-lanka-processing-chinas-request-for-research-ship-docking-that-may-raise-security-concerns-in-india%2Farticle67226203.ece%5C%22%3Etold%C2%A0PTI%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20ship%20is%20expected%20to%20undertake%20research%20jointly%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20National%20Aquatic%20Resources%20Research%20and%20Development%20Agency%20(NARA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20a%20visit%20by%20a%20Chinese%20ballistic%20missile%20and%20satellite%20tracking%20ship%2C%20%3Cem%3EYuan%20Wang%205%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20arrived%20in%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20port%20of%20Hambantota%20led%20to%20a%20sharp%20set%20of%20responses%20from%20India.%20Concerns%20were%20expressed%20about%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20ship%20to%20engage%20in%20surveillance%20of%20Indian%20marine%20assets%20while%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHambantota%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%E2%80%9D%20port%20in%20southern%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20has%20been%20built%20by%20a%20Chinese%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695188627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20111315%2F6136c82cc6d0df5736872b7c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchinese-research-ship-given-permission-to-dock-at-sri-lankan-port-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shi%20Yan%206%20had%20caused%20concern%20in%20India%20about%20its%20ability%20to%20surveil%20Indian%20assets%20while%20roaming%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20The%20ship%20is%20reported%20to%20dock%20on%20September%2029%2C%20according%20to%20Sri%20Lankan%20news%20outlets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchinese-research-ship-given-permission-to-dock-at-sri-lankan-port-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Is%20Canada-Based%20Rapper%20Shubh%20In%20News%3F%20Controversy%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanada-based%20Punjabi%20singer%20Shubhneet%20Singh%2C%20popularly%20known%20by%20his%20stage%20name%20Shubh%2C%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20controversy%20for%20his%20alleged%20support%20for%20Khalistan.%20This%20controversial%20issue%20has%20been%20straining%20relations%20between%20Canada%20and%20India.%20The%20singer%2C%20who%20has%20risen%20to%20fame%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20with%20hits%20like%20%26quot%3BElevated%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BOG%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCheques%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20a%20massive%20fanbase%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2019%2C%20electronics%20brand%20boAt%20retracted%20its%20sponsorship%20of%20the%20upcoming%20India%20tour%20of%20the%20singer.%20BoAt's%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20its%20sponsorship%20is%20primarily%20rooted%20in%20the%20singer's%20controversial%20actions%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20he%20shared%20a%20distorted%20map%20of%20India%20on%20his%20Instagram%20story%2C%20conspicuously%20omitting%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20the%20Northeastern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20picture%2C%20the%20singer%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BPray%20for%20Punjab%26quot%3B%2C%20for%20which%20he%20was%20slammed%20massively%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20singer%20later%20deleted%20the%20map%20and%20replaced%20it%20with%20a%20message%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BPray%20for%20Punjab%26quot%3B%20without%20any%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fboat-withdraws-sponsorship-for-canadian-punjabi-singer-shubhs-india-tour-over-controversial-remarks-4404993%5C%22%3EBoAt%20Withdraws%20Sponsorship%20For%20Canadian%20Singer's%20India%20Tour%20Over%20Controversial%20Remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20singer%20is%20scheduled%20to%20perform%20in%20Mumbai%20from%20September%2023-25%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Cruise%20Control%204.0%20event%2C%20organised%20aboard%20the%20Cordelia%20Cruise.%20He%20will%20also%20perform%20in%20cities%20such%20as%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Hyderabad.%20However%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Yuva%20Morcha%20(BJYM)%2C%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20BJP%20removed%20posters%20promoting%20his%20concert%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20'Khalistan'%20supporters%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20space%20for%20Khalistanis%20who%20are%20the%20enemy%20of%20integrity%20and%20unity%20of%20India.%20We%20won't%20let%20Canadian%20singer%20Shubh%20perform%20on%20the%20auspicious%20land%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%2C%20Mumbai...If%20no%20proper%20action%20is%20taken%20then%20the%20organisers%20will%20have%20to%20face%20the%20revolt...%26quot%3B%20BJYM%20President%20Tajinder%20Singh%20Tiwana%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20controversy%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20along%20with%20fellow%20cricketers%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20unfollowed%20the%20singer%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20singer's%20tour%20unfolds%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20strained%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%20Canada%20on%20Monday%20accused%20the%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20and%20expelled%20New%20Delhi's%20intelligence%20chief%20in%20Ottawa%20in%20retaliation.%20The%20diplomatic%20move%20sent%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20already%20sour%2C%20to%20a%20dramatic%20new%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20rejected%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20government's%20allegation%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%20reciprocal%20move%2C%20India%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20and%20gave%20him%205%20days%20to%20leave%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695188580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fefrioaeo_shubh_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-is-canada-based-rapper-shubh-in-news-controversy-explained-4406061%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20singer%2C%20who%20has%20risen%20to%20fame%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20with%20hits%20like%20%26quot%3BElevated%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BOG%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCheques%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20a%20massive%20fanbase%20across%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-is-canada-based-rapper-shubh-in-news-controversy-explained-4406061%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-is-canada-based-rapper-shubh-in-news-controversy-explained-4406061%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-is-canada-based-rapper-shubh-in-news-controversy-explained-4406061%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India-Canada%20Diplomatic%20Spat%20Worries%20Students%2C%20Immigrant%20Visa%20Applicants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14132814%2F41.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20escalation%20of%20diplomatic%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20has%20already%20begun%20to%20worry%20a%20number%20of%20Indians%2C%20including%20students%2C%20who%20head%20to%20the%20North%20American%20country%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEducational%20consultancies%20working%20with%20students%20in%20India%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20ongoing%20diplomatic%20spat%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20would%20further%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20complication%20to%20an%20already%20difficult%20immigration%20process.%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Canada%20is%20the%20second%20most%20preferred%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students%20overseas%2C%20it%20has%20tightened%20its%20visa%20rules%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECompanies%20with%20tie-ups%20with%20offices%20in%20Canada%20are%20equally%20worried%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20heightened%20level%20of%20scrutiny%20of%20applications%20from%20states%20such%20as%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20making%20it%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20immigrant%20visa%20applications%20to%20be%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20show%20up%20in%20the%20visa%20approvals%20in%20the%20long%20term.%20The%20success%20ratio%20of%20student%20visas%20for%20Canada%20is%20just%2060%25%20and%20may%20come%20down%20further.%20Students%20focusing%20on%20just%20Canada%20need%20to%20keep%20other%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELiveMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdiplomatic-strain-raises-visa-worries-11695150332988.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ankur%20Dhawan%2C%20president%20of%20upGrad%20Abroad%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20students%2C%20it%20is%20those%20Indians%20applying%20for%20immigrant%20visas%20who%20might%20have%20to%20face%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20present%20crisis%20in%20India-Canada%20bilateral%20ties.%20%E2%80%9CImmigration%20visas%20will%20be%20a%20larger%20concern%20than%20student%20visas.%20Canadian%20authorities%20increased%20their%20scrutiny%20over%20the%20last%20year%20on%20applicants%E2%80%99%20documents%2C%20and%20now%20that%20will%20increase%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ankit%20Mehra%2C%20co-founder%20and%20chief%20executive%20of%20GyanDhan%2C%20a%20non-banking%20financial%20company%20(NBFC).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NBFC%20representative%20further%20said%20they%20have%20seen%20a%20three-fold%20rise%20in%20loan%20applications%20from%20those%20preferring%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20good%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%202021-23.%20However%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Punjab%20has%20seen%20a%20fivefold%20increase%20since%202021.%20Outside%20of%20Punjab%2C%20most%20Punjabis%20live%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20Indians%20who%20prefer%20Canada%20explore%20work%20options%20in%20entry-level%20jobs%20and%20mid-level%20positions%20in%20a%20range%20of%20fields%2C%20including%20retail%2C%20business%20services%2C%20and%20manufacturing.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20students%20take%20higher%20education%20courses%20in%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20medical%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImmigration%20visas%20may%20get%20restricted%20since%20the%20Canadian%20government%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20has%20stressed%20that%20they%20prefer%20students%20to%20come%20in%2C%20acclimatise%20into%20the%20ecosystem%20and%20then%20settle%20down.%20Some%20of%20the%20Indian%20states%20will%20see%20more%20scrutiny%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Akshay%20Chaturvedi%2C%20founder%20and%20chief%20executive%20of%20Leverage%20Edu%2C%20which%20ties%20up%20with%20banks%20and%20NBFCs%20to%20help%20students%20who%20go%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20hope%20that%20the%20Canadian%20government%20may%20not%20immediately%20bring%20in%20any%20curbs%20on%20visas%2C%20particularly%20for%20students%2C%20there%20is%20a%20fear%20that%20the%20escalation%20of%20hostilities%2C%20however%2C%20could%20make%20it%20an%20eventuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20alleged%20a%20possible%20Indian%20government%20link%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20their%20citizen%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20both%20countries%20responded%20by%20expelling%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20diplomats.%20While%20India%20dismissed%20the%20charge%2C%20Canada%20said%20it%20would%20seek%20the%20support%20of%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20to%20pursue%20the%20matter%20against%20India%20at%20a%20global%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695188181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14132814%2F41.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Findia-canada-diplomatic-spat-worries-students-immigrant-visa-applicants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20is%20the%20second%20most%20preferred%20destination%20for%20higher%20education%20among%20Indian%20students%2C%20particularly%20for%20those%20from%20Punjab%20and%20H