ste%20composter%3C%2Fa%3E%20possesses%20an%20impressive%20capability%20of%20%E2%80%9Cseamlessly%20converting%E2%80%9D%20waste%20amounting%20to%20anywhere%20between%2020%20kg%20to%2010%20tonnes%20into%20%E2%80%98nutrient-rich%20compost%E2%80%99%20in%20just%20eight%20hours%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20emitting%20harmful%20emissions%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESandeep%20Tiwari%2C%20founder%20of%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies%2C%20calls%20the%20Gold%20Composter%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmarvel%20of%20waste%20management%20technology%E2%80%9D.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20innovation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20We%20have%20the%20expertise%20and%20versatility%20to%20design%20and%20implement%20large%20composters%20that%20can%20process%20hundreds%20of%20tons%20of%20organic%20waste%20in%20a%20single%20day%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20Tiwari%2C%20CEO%20of%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWaste-Is-Gold-Technologies-CEO-1695133545-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330329%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Tiwari%2C%20CEO%20of%20Waste%20Is%20Gold%20Technologies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Does%20It%20Work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tiwari%2C%20the%20Gold%20Composter%20is%20an%20advanced%20aerobic%20organic%20waste%20composter%20which%20%E2%80%9Cemploys%20a%20completely%20natural%20bio-mechanical%20process%2C%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20our%20proprietary%20bacteria%20and%20bioreactor%20technology%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20breaks%20down%20organic%20waste%20rapidly%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20excessive%20heating%20and%20ensuring%20that%20no%20harmful%20emissions%20like%20methane%20are%20released%20into%20the%20environment.%20This%20results%20in%20a%20composting%20process%20with%20a%20low%20carbon%20footprint.%20Operating%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20aerobic%20decomposition%2C%20this%20cutting-edge%20technology%20employs%20oxygen-consuming%20microorganisms%20and%20bio-reactor%20to%20accelerate%20the%20breakdown%20of%20organic%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20machine%20facilitates%20aerobic%20composting%20by%20meticulously%20maintaining%20the%20ideal%20temperature%2C%20air%2C%20oxygen%2C%20and%20moisture%20conditions%2C%20guaranteeing%20a%20fast%20and%20efficient%20transformation%20of%20organic%20waste.%20Our%20organic%20waste%20composter%20output%20requires%20no%20further%20processing.%20It%20can%20be%20directly%20placed%20into%20aerated%20crates%20for%20storage%2C%20ready%20for%20later%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20Tiwari%20recommends%20allowing%20the%20compost%20to%20fully%20mature%20for%20three%20to%20seven%20days%20after%20processing%2C%20ensuring%20it%20reaches%20its%20peak%20nutrient%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20for%20landscaping%20and%20gardening%20needs%2C%20the%20compost%20can%20be%20utilised%20on%20the%20same%20day%20it%E2%80%99s%20produced%2C%20providing%20an%20instant%20boost%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318062%2Fiit-bombay-scientist-dr-rajul-patkar-innovates-portable-soil-testing-device-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20composter%20can%20treat%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20organic%20waste%20types%20%E2%80%94%20including%20cooked%20food%20waste%2C%20organic%20wet%20waste%2C%20bones%2C%20meat%2C%20feathers%2C%20eggshells%2C%20vegetable%20waste%2C%20tender%20coconut%2C%20horticulture%20waste%2C%20grass%20clippings%2C%20tissue%20paper%2C%20STP%20sludge%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20waste%20to%20compost%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Solid%20Waste%20Management%20Policy%202016%20mandates%20that%20bulk%20waste%20generators%20take%20responsibility%20for%20processing%20their%20waste%20right%20at%20their%20own%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20complements%20this%20policy%20seamlessly.%20By%20deploying%20our%20aerobic%20composter%20directly%20at%20our%20client%E2%80%99s%20premises%2C%20we%20empower%20bulk%20waste%20generators%20to%20comply%20with%20government%20directives.%20This%20not%20only%20eases%20the%20burden%20on%20landfills%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20We%20stand%20as%20reliable%20partners%20for%20communities%2C%20organisations%2C%20urban%20local%20bodies%20and%20institutions%20in%20their%20journey%20towards%20responsible%20waste%20management%20practices%20and%20help%20them%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Tiwari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20feeding%20organic%20waste%20into%20their%20Gold%20Composter%2C%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20their%20process