much%20nicer%20if%20the%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20could%20have%20taken%20the%20trouble%20to%20announce%20this%20in%20both%20the%20Houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20strange%20reason%2C%20members%20of%20both%20Houses%20were%20summoned%20to%20the%20central%20lawns%20of%20the%20(old)%20parliament%20on%20September%2019%20morning%20for%20a%20joint%20photograph.%20A%20semi-circular%20gallery%2C%20with%20several%20levels%2C%20was%20in%20place%20but%20we%20had%20not%20heard%20of%20any%20large-scale%20departure%20of%20members%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20to%20warrant%20a%20group%20photo.%20Neither%20was%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20slated%20to%20be%20prorogued%20or%20dissolved%20without%20holding%20the%20winter%20and%20budget%20sessions%20till%20February%20and%20March%202024%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20there%20are%20plans%20to%20hold%20elections%20earlier.%20The%20point%20is%20that%20September%20is%20the%20cruelest%20month%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20hot%2C%20sweaty%20and%20searingly%20sunny.%20Members%20squeezed%20together%20and%20perched%20themselves%20on%20the%20precarious%20layered%20platform%20%E2%80%98tiers%E2%80%99%2C%20holding%20on%20to%20each%20other%2C%20and%20put%20up%20with%20the%20rather-asphyxiating%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20waiting%2C%20waiting%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20VIPs%20to%20arrive.%20One%20poor%20MP%20had%20an%20emergency%20as%20he%20simply%20swooned%20and%20collapsed%2C%20as%C2%A0he%20could%20take%20it%20no%20more.%20Fellow%20MPs%20clambered%20to%20hold%20him%20lest%20he%20fall%20down%2C%20from%20a%20height%20of%20some%20eight%20or%20ten%20feet.%20As%20soon%20as%20matters%20settled%20down%20a%20bit%2C%20the%20agony%20of%20taking%20two%20photographs%2C%20first%20with%20all%20MPs%20and%20the%20second%20of%20individual%20Houses%2C%20was%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Entering%20the%20Temple%20of%20Democracy%20For%20the%20Last%20Time%3A%20A%20Parliament%20Journalist's%20Account%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fparliament-new-building-journalism-politics-mps%5C%22%3EEntering%20the%20Temple%20of%20Democracy%20For%20the%20Last%20Time%3A%20A%20Parliament%20Journalist%E2%80%99s%20Account%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMembers%20moved%20across%20the%20lawn%2C%20gulping%20as%20much%20water%20as%20they%20could%2C%20to%20beat%20the%20dehydration.%20They%20rushed%20to%20take%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20packed%20%E2%80%98central%20hall%E2%80%99.%20This%20would%20possibly%20be%20the%20last%20ever%20meeting%20in%20this%20grand%20historic%20chamber%20where%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20had%20been%20framed%2C%20clause%20by%20clause.%20This%20been%20the%20only%20place%20where%20members%2C%20ex-members%2C%20ministers%2C%20former%20ministers%20and%20senior%20journalists%20met%20and%20discussed%20so%20many%20issues%20for%20the%20last%2075%20years.%20This%20is%20where%20tea%2C%20coffee%20and%20light%20refreshments%20were%20served%20as%20political%20leaders%20of%20different%20hues%20and%20from%20distant%20states%20shared%20%3Cem%3Epakoda%3C%2Fem%3Es%20and%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3Es%20%E2%80%94%20often%20after%20animated%20debates%20in%20the%20Houses.%20But%20this%20day%20was%20different%2C%20for%20we%20would%20never%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20sit%20amidst%20these%20historic%20yet%20cosy%20surroundings%20and%20sort%20more%20problems%20than%20any%20regime%20could%20ever%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20and%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20trooped%20in%2C%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20leader%20in%20the%20Upper%20House%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20opposition%20of%20both%20houses.%20The%20leaders%20spoke%20on%20expected%20lines%20but%20without%20acrimony.%20To%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20surprise%2C%20Maneka%20Gandhi%20was%20specially%20invited%20to%20speak%2C%20ostensibly%20as%20one%20who%20had%20been%20elected%20seven%20times%2C%20and%20also%20perhaps%20to%20rile%20another%20lady.%20Then%20came%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20longish%20speech%2C%20full%20of%20high%20sounding%20phrases%20and%20promises%20and%20a%20grand%20periscopic%20vision%20for%20India.%20So%20full%20of%20catch-words%20and%20buzz%20phrases%2C%20supplied%20almost%20certainly%20by%20high-end%20advertising%20and%20PR%20agencies%2C%20was%20it%20that%20anyone%20who%20was%20not%20fully%20aware%20of%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20of%202002%20and%20the%20sustained%20lynchings%20from%202014%20onward%20would%20surely%20have%20fallen%20for%20it.%20As%20he%20looked%20frequently%20at%20his%20notes%20(teleprompters%20are%20not%20allowed)%20and%20paused%2C%20loud%2C%20very%20loud%2C%20thumping%20of%20desks%20followed.%20It%20was%20so%20mechanical%20and%20unreal%20but%20one%20was%20reminded%20of%20an%20old%20party%20hand.%20He%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CKeep%20cheering.%20clapping%20and%20thumping%20desks%2C%20as%20no%20one%20know%20who%20is%20keeping%20track%20of%20your%20expressions%20of%20loyalty%2C%20or%20the%20visible%20lack%20of%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20084201%2FF6Y-Q-KbYAAuxQS.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20084201%2FF6Y-Q-KbYAAuxQS.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20084201%2FF6Y-Q-KbYAAuxQS-300x216.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20084201%2FF6Y-Q-KbYAAuxQS-1024x736.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673847%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20greets%20MPs%20in%20the%20central%20hall%20of%20the%20old%20parliament%20building.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20did%20make%20a%20rare%20reference%20to%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tryst%20with%20destiny%E2%80%99%20speech%2C%20which%20is%20most%20unusual%20of%20him%20and%20his%20inspired%20vitriolic%20campaign%20against%20the%20first%20prime%20minister.%20But%20his%20orator%20failed%20to%20reach%20anywhere%20near%20its%20immortal%20status.%20Nehru%20had%2C%20after%20all%2C%20toiled%20with%20and%20for%20the%20masses%20for%20over%20quarter%20a%20century%20and%20had%20been%20in%20jail%20for%20nine%20long%20years.%20This%20was%20a%20background%20that%20Modi%20could%20never%20hope%20to%20match%2C%20even%20if%20one%20leaves%20aside%20levels%20of%20education%20and%20world%20views.%20Modi%20had%20summoned%20both%20Houses%20to%20this%20central%20hall%20at%20midnight%20in%20June%202017%2C%20once%20before%2C%20emulating%20Nehru%2C%20when%20he%20introduced%20GST%20amidst%20yawns%20%E2%80%93%20both%20stifled%20and%20not-so-suppressed%20ones.%20But%20this%20GST%20gambit%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20damp%20squib%20then%20and%20caused%20immense%20problems.%20He%20made%20yet%20another%20attempt%20today%2C%20and%20this%2C%20too%2C%20was%20even%20more%20damp.%20Several%20of%20those%20who%20spoke%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20obvious%20thrall%20of%20Modi%20%E2%80%94%20a%20view%20that%20is%20hardly%20shared%20by%20many%20others%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20owe%20their%20positions%20to%20him.%20Some%2C%20naturally%2C%20gushed%20forth%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20hyperbole%2C%20but%20they%20could%20not%20rescue%20a%20non-event.%20Unless%20the%20prime%20minister%20drops%20a%20bombshell%20on%20some%20other%20matter%20soon%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20he%20has%20called%20an%20expensive%20%E2%80%98special%20session%E2%80%99%20of%20parliament%20largely%20to%20procure%20a%20captive%20audience%20of%20all%20MPs%2C%20to%20witness%20his%20great%20event.%20This%20highly%20pumped-up%20ceremony%20was%20marking%20the%20transfer%20of%20parliament%20from%20one%20building%20to%20the%20other%2C%20just%20a%20few%20feet%20apart.%20There%20was%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20not%20a%20word%20on%20Manipur%20or%20other%20burning%20problems%3B%20this%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20and%20he%20determined%20its%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECeremony%20over%2C%20a%20small%20group%20of%20ministers%20were%20led%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20into%20the%20only%20edifice%20that%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20thrust%20upon%20Delhi%2C%20despite%20his%20loud%20proclamations%20%E2%80%94%20other%20than%20the%20new%20%3Cem%3EBharat%20Mandapam%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehall%20that%20he%20rushed%20through%20in%20Pragati%20Maidan%20to%20impress%20his%20G20%20guests.%20One%20cannot%20comment%20on%20the%20latter%20building%2C%20as%20all%20one%20remembers%20is%20the%20the%20blinding%20magenta%20colour%20that%20the%20TV%20focused%20on%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpib-says-some-claims-of-waterlogging-at-g20-venue-misleading-and-exaggerated%5C%22%3Einstant%20flooding%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20one%20sharp%20shower%20bestowed%20upon%20it.%20But%20the%20thick%20veil%20over%20the%20over-secretive%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20lifted%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20had%20said%20before%2C%20its%20main%20entrance%20looks%20like%20just%20one%20more%20movie%20theatre%20or%20a%20mid-sized%20shopping%20complex.%20The%20%E2%80%98sacred%20animals%E2%80%99%20sculpted%20(or%20assembled)%20in%20red%20sandstone%20at%20each%20gate%2C%20with%20names%20both%20familiar%20and%20bizarrely%20unfamiliar%2C%20are%20supposed%20to%20mark%20the%20several%20gates%2C%20most%20of%20which%20remained%20shut%20on%20the%20first%20day.%20There%20is%20nothing%20that%20distinguishes%20the%20corridors%20and%20lobbies%20in%20the%20new%20building%20from%20one%20more%20five-star%20hotel.%20Yes%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20glitz%20has%20been%20grafted%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20aesthetics%2C%20but%20then%2C%20the%20latter%20requires%20instinct%2C%20training%20and%20upbringing.%20There%20is%20no%20central%20hall%20and%20the%20two%20Houses%20are%20kept%20far%20apart%2C%20with%20separate%20canteens%20that%20are%20no%20better%20that%20most%20ordinary%20caf%C3%A9s.%20The%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20huge%2C%20unnecessary%20so%2C%20and%20the%20last%20two%20long%20rows%20appeared%20empty.%20The%20atrium%20is%20far%20too%20high%20and%20instead%20of%20raising%20both%20the%20eyes%20and%20the%20soul%20upwards%2C%20they%20remind%20one%20of%20massive%20electric%20bills.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20even%20bigger%20and%20can%20accommodate%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20double%20up%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98central%20hall%E2%80%99%20in%20terms%20of%20space%2C%20but%20neither%20in%20warmth%20nor%20in%20genuineness.%20There%20is%20a%20cold%2C%20corporate%20sense%20of%20distancing%20that%20even%20the%20imperial%20old%20parliament%20never%20conveyed.%20It%20carried%20an%20aura%20and%20a%20gravitas%20that%20this%20one%20can%20hardly%20acquire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20came%20in%20and%20gave%20yet%20another%20rise-above-politics%20speech%20glibly%20and%20with%20a%20poker%20face.%20It%20was%2C%20mercifully%2C%20shorter%20than%20the%20earlier%20sermon.%20But%20his%20very%20presence%20excites%20divisions%20and%20the%20Treasury%20benches%20started%20shouting%20at%20a%20remark%20made%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition.%20The%20chairman%20had%20a%20tough%20time%20to%20maintain%20order.%20This%20rough%20and%20unpleasant%20exchange%20of%20words%20and%20charges%20between%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20was%20on%20%E2%80%98day%20one%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20benign%20and%20somewhat%20indulgent%20presence%20of%20the%20prime%20minister.%20It%20leads%20us%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20one%20can%20splurge%20public%20money%20to%20seek%20immortality%20but%20the%20searing%20gashes%20in%20politics%20will%20remain%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20is%20the%20spirit%20of%2