h%20Chouhan-led%20BJP%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Clost%20its%20way%E2%80%9D%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20to%20return%20it%20to%20power.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20no%20longer%20going%20to%20support%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20whatever%20reason%2C%20be%20it%20self-interest%20or%20ticket%2C%20people%20are%20joining%20the%20Congress.%20The%20public%20cannot%20ignore%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20element%20of%20truth%20in%20his%20statement.%20In%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20several%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20big%20and%20small%2C%20have%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20joined%20the%20Congress%2C%20some%20with%20plenty%20of%20fanfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20estimates%20put%20the%20number%20at%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20the%20sitting%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Kolaras%20in%20Shivpuri%2C%20Virendra%20Raghuvanshi%3B%20former%20MLA%20Bhanwar%20Singh%20Shekhawat%3B%20former%20MP%20from%20Khargone%20Makhansingh%20Solanki%3B%20and%20three-time%20former%20MLA%20and%20former%20cabinet%20minister%20Deepak%20Joshi.%20Like%20Sharma%2C%20Joshi%20also%20ended%20a%20long-running%2C%20close-knit%20relationship%20with%20the%20saffron%20party.%20His%20father%20Kailash%20Chandra%20Joshi%20was%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20and%20an%20important%20Jan%20Sangh%20leader%20with%20an%20illustrious%20public%20life.%20The%20senior%20Joshi%20won%20the%20assembly%20election%20from%20Bagri%20seat%20eight%20times%2C%20apart%20from%20winning%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Bhopal%20and%20being%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20joining%20the%20Congress%2C%20Deepak%20Joshi%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20persecuting%20party%20workers%20who%20were%20following%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20path.%20He%20also%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20diminishing%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Joshi%20lost%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%20from%20the%20Hatpipaliya%20seat%20in%20Dewas%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Manoj%20Narayansingh%20Choudhari.%20In%20March%202020%2C%2022%20Congress%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20led%20by%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20%E2%80%93%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20toppled%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChoudhari%20was%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20by-poll%20necessitated%20by%20the%20defections%2C%20the%20BJP%20fielded%20Choudhari%20instead%20of%20Joshi.%20The%20former%20won%20the%20by-poll%2C%20putting%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20political%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20defeat%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan%20if%20Party%20gives%20me%20tickets%2C%20Deepak%20Joshi%20after%20joining%20Congress.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20leadership%20is%20collapsing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoevgA96Fil%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FoevgA96Fil%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Shantanu%20(%40shaandelhite)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshaandelhite%2Fstatus%2F1654772882021416961%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMLA%20Raghuvanshi%20from%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region%20blamed%20the%20new%20entrants%20led%20by%20Scindia%20for%20his%20disenchantment%20with%20the%20BJP.%20While%20announcing%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20Raghuvanshi%20said%20%E2%80%9Coriginal%E2%80%9D%20BJP%20workers%20like%20him%20were%20being%20harassed%20and%20that%20he%20was%20not%20even%20being%20allowed%20to%20conduct%20the%20ground-breaking%20ceremony%20or%20inauguration%20of%20development%20projects%20sanctioned%20by%20him%20as%20legislator.%20He%20said%20former%20Congress%20MLA%20Mahendra%20Yadav%20was%20acting%20like%20his%20superior%20after%20joining%20the%20BJP%20along%20with%20Scindia.%20In%202018%2C%20Raghuvanshi%20had%20defeated%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20informed%20the%20party%20leadership%20that%20it%20was%20a%20good%20thing%20to%20have%20formed%20the%20government%20%5Bin%202020%5D%2C%20but%20one%20should%20not%20raise%20the%20%3Cem%3Evarchasva%3C%2Fem%3E%20(domination)%20of%20one%20person%20%5BScindia%5D%20to%20such%20heights%20that%20we%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20carry%20out%20development%20and%20public%20service%20and%20to%20remain%20in%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raghuvanshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOthers%20who%20have%20shifted%20loyalties%20include%20former%20MLA%20from%20Datia%20Radhelal%20Baghel%3B%20Rao%20Yadvendra%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20former%20zilla%20panchayat%20chairman%20and%20son%20of%20a%20three-time%20MLA%3B%20Anubha%20Munjare%2C%20wife%20of%20former%20Balaghat%20MP%20Kankar%20Munjare%3B%20Malkhan%20Singh%2C%20a%20dacoit-turned-Narendra%20Modi%20campaigner%3B%20Ashish%20Agarwal%2C%20former%20state%20home%20minister%20Umashankar%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20nephew%3B%20and%20Megha%20Parmar%2C%20ace%20mountaineer%20and%20the%20first%20woman%20from%20MP%20to%20climb%20Mt%20Everest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20dropped%20her%20as%20the%20state%20ambassador%20for%20the%20Beti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%20programme.%20The%20list%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20have%20joined%20the%20Congress%20also%20includes%20those%20who%20were%20considered%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Scindia.%20The%20latest%20among%20them%20was%20Samandar%20Patel%2C%20who%20led%20a%20convoy%20of%20700-800%20vehicles%20from%20his%20hometown%20in%20Neemuch%20to%20Bhopal%2C%20where%20he%20joined%20the%20Congress.%20In%20July%2C%20another%20Scindia%20loyalist%20who%20had%20followed%20him%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20Baijnath%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20former%20Congress%20Shivpuri%20president%2C%20returned%20to%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Kamal%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20defections%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhether%20they%20were%20disgruntled%20due%20to%20roadblocks%20in%20their%20personal%20ambitions%2C%20insecure%20over%20getting%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20or%20have%20personal%20scores%20to%20settle%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20by%20quitting%20the%20BJP%20and%20joining%20the%20Congress%20these%20leaders%20have%20provided%20the%20latter%20with%20the%20edge%20in%20the%20perception%20battle%20as%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20heads%20towards%20an%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20rebellions%20have%20also%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20internal%20rifts%20and%20churning%20within%20the%20BJP%20and%20a%20new%20element%20of%20factionalism%20driven%20by%20the%20entry%20of%20Scindia%20and%20his%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20Chouhan%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20government%20for%20most%20of%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20state%20BJP%20also%20has%20other%20senior%20leaders%20like%20state%20president%20and%20MP%20V.D.%20Sharma%2C%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20state%20home%20minister%20Narottam%20Mishra%20%E2%80%93%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20Scindia%20%E2%80%93%20who%20command%20their%20own%20set%20of%20loyalists.%20If%20political%20observers%20are%20to%20be%20relied%20upon%2C%20all%20of%20these%20leaders%20also%20harbour%20greater%20ambition.%20The%20entry%20of%20Scindia%20and%20his%20loyalists%20in%20particular%20seems%20to%20have%20caused%20discontent%20among%20a%20section%20of%20BJP%20old-timers%2C%20workers%20and%20leaders%20alike.%20In%20public%2C%20however%2C%20the%20party%20puts%20up%20a%20united%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGirija%20Shanker%20Sharma%2C%20who%20was%20with%20the%20BJP%20till%20recently%2C%20says%20there%20is%20dissatisfaction%20among%20these%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20over%20securing%20tickets%20for%20their%20loyalists.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20some%20meaningful%20discontent%20over%20policies%20or%20programmes%20but%20mutual%20conflict%20over%20tickets%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObservers%20say%20it%20is%20not%20certain%20that%20Chouhan%20would%20be%20retained%20as%20the%20CM%20if%20the%20BJP%20does%20win.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20other%20aspirants%20are%20trying%20to%20build%20up%20their%20own%20support%20bases%20among%20probable%20legislators%20to%20stake%20a%20claim%20for%20the%20top%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13192647%2FF0g9YnHagAEuCqI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22847%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13192647%2FF0g9YnHagAEuCqI.jpeg%20847w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13192647%2FF0g9YnHagAEuCqI-300x160.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663068%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22453%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40ChouhanShivraj%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20tried%20to%20project%20the%20defections%20from%20the%20BJP%20as%20panic%20setting%20in.%20The%20influx%20of%20leaders%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20the%20Congress%20has%20produced%20two%20results%2C%20says%20Paras%20Saklecha%2C%20a%20former%20independent%20MLA%20who%20joined%20the%20Congress%20in%202018%20and%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20anti-corruption%20crusade%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20since%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20able%20to%20snatch%20some%20core%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20it%20has%20sent%20a%20message%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20projection%20of%20itself%20as%20a%20disciplined%20organisation%20no%20longer%20holds.%20The%20party%20organisation%20is%20not%20as%20strong%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be%20or%20as%20it%20projects%20itself%20to%20be%2C%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrict%20central%20leader%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20dissipated%2C%20claims%20Saklecha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20whether%20these%20leaders%20quit%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20election%20tickets%20or%20not%2C%20what%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20public%20is%20that%20these%20turncoats%20see%20their%20future%20secure%20in%20the%20Congress%20as%20they%20believe%20it%20has%20a%20greater%20chance%20of%20coming%20to%20power.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20atmosphere%20building%20up%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saklecha%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Saklecha%20was%20standing%20next%20to%20Kamal%20Nath%20when%20he%20released%20an%20%3Cem%3Eaarop%20patra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chargesheet)%20of%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20scams%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20%E2%80%93%20a%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%9CGhotala%20hi%20Ghotala%E2%80%94Ghotala%20seth%2C%2050%25%20commission%20rate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Chouhan%20as%20%E2%80%9CLootera%20Mama%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20document%20included%20details%20of%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20financial%20and%20governance%20matters%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20in%20over%20225%20%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D.%20This%20included%20the%20infamous%20Vyapam%20scam%2C%20and%20irregularities%20in%20Poshan%20Ahar%20and%20mid-day%20meal%20schemes%2C%20Anganwadi%20department%2C%20tap-water%2C%20Patwari%20recruitment%2C%20nursing%2C%20para-medical%20scholarship%2C%20illegal%20mining%2C%20tribal%20land%20and%20Mahakal%20Lok%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLA%20from%20Dhar%20Hiralal%20Alawa%20says%20the%20defection%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20has%20strengthened%20the%20mood%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20see%20leaders%20leaving%20the%20ruling%20party%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Alawa%2C%20who%20is%20from%20a%20tribal%20community.%20The%20MLA%20also%20claims%20that%20there%20is%20growing%20disenchantment%20among%20the%20sizeable%20tribal%20communities%2C%20which%20constitute%2021%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20towards%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20because%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20cloud%20over%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20and%20the%20recent%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20Brahmin%20man%20linked%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-man-urinate-tribal-youth-viral-video%5C%22%3Eurinated%20upon%20a%20man%20from%20a%20tribal%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Sidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20about%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20leadership%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20timely%20opportunism%20during%20election%20season%20and%20shifting%20of%20loyalties%20are%20endemic%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20senior%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst%20Girija%20Shanker%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20noticeable%20trend%20this%20time%20around.%20%E2%80%9CLeaders%20shift%20from%20one%20party%20to%20another%20before%20every%20election.%20These%20are%20never%20about%20policies%20but%20about%20exploring%20new%20opportunities.%20But%20the%20difference%20this%20time%20is%20that%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20and%20not%20the%20BJP%20that%20is%20doing%20this%20to%20build%20an%20atmosphere%20in%20its%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shanker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20analyst%2C%20however%2C%20also%20cautions%20that%20barring%20one%20sitting%20MLA%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20ex-legislators%2C%20none%20of%20those%20who%20have%20quit%20the%20BJP%20have%20a%20personal%20mass%20following%20or%20are%20influential%20on%20their%20own.%20He%20also%20says%20that%20given%20the%20strong%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20infighting%20and%20factionalism%20in%20MP%20would%20not%20become%20a%20big%20factor%20in%20the%20election%20and%20would%20be%20likely%20brought%20under%20control.%20Hidden%20discontent%20within%20the%20party%20ranks%20might%20prove%20more%20detrimental%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20continued%20defections%20have%20also%20raised%20a%20question%20about%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20has%20never%20looked%20as%20vulnerable%20as%20he%20has%20in%20this%20election%20season.%20Saklecha%2C%20who%20had%20made%20life%20difficult%20for%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20previous%20governments%20by%20raising%20the%20Vyapam%20scam%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20says%20the%20CM%20is%20showing%20signs%20of%20nervousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20doubt%20%5Bfrom%5D%20his%20body%20language%20%5Bthat%20he%20is%20under%20pressure%5D.%20He%20is%20being%20over-active.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20speeches%2C%20while%20referring%20to%20the%20newly%20launched%20Ladli-Behna%20scheme%2C%20he%20repeatedly%20asked%20the%20crowd%20if%20they%20liked%20the%20scheme.%20He%20was%20almost%20persuading%20them%20to%20say%20yes.%20He%20was%20not%20confident%20that%20the%20public%20was%20taking%20it%20positively%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Saklecha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Chaturvedi%2C%20a%20Scindia-loyalist%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202020%20and%20is%20today%20a%20party%20spokesperson%2C%20however%2C%20says%20the%20defections%20are%20but%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%20joy%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Congress.%20He%20downplays%20the%20trend%20of%20Scindia%20loyalists%20returning%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20saying%20it%20does%20not%20impact%20the%20leader%E2%80%99s%20image%20or%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20also%20dismissed%20the%20trend%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20joining%20the%20Congress%2C%20saying%20that%20only%20those%20who%20had%20realised%20that%20they%20would%20not%20get%20a%20ticket%20were%20leaving.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20public%20is%20not%20bothered%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Asked%20specifically%20if%20Scindia%20had%20chief%20ministerial%20aspirations%20and%20if%20factionalism%20in%20the%20BJP%20would%20hurt%20its%20interests%2C%20Chaturvedi%20said%20that%20from%20day%20one%2C%20Scindia%20had%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20it%20clear%20that%20his%20motive%20was%20not%20to%20achieve%20political%20chair%20or%20CM%20post%20but%20to%20serve%20the%20public%20through%20a%20nationalist%20vision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFactionalism%20was%20actually%20rampant%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20Chaturvedi%20claimed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20is%20a%20divided%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20claiming%20that%20senior%20leaders%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20Ajay%20Singh%2C%20Arun%20Yadav%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20and%20Jitu%20Patwari%20all%20had%20some%20quota%20of%20seats%20to%20be%20allotted%20to%20their%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20when%20the%20same%20questions%20were%20put%20forward%20to%20Scindia%20by%20an%20Aaj%20Tak%20anchor%20at%20the%20channel%E2%80%99s%20election%20conclave%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20the%20leader%20downplayed%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20a%20CM%20candidate%20and%20was%20not%20one%20even%20then%20%5Bin%202018%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Scindia%20said.%20On%20his%20loyalists%20returning%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20be%20diplomatic%20and%20interpreted%20it%20as%20people%E2%80%99s%20display%20of%20personal%20aspirations.%20He%20even%20wished%20them%20all%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20elections%20are%20near%2C%20say%20two%20or%20three%20months%20left%2C%20this%20%3Cem%3Eavagaman%20ki%20neeti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(practice%20of%20movement%20of%20leaders%20into%20and%20away%20from%20parties)%20is%20common.%20If%20one%20feels%20they%20will%20not%20get%20a%20ticket%20here%20but%20there%2C%20then%20that%20sets%20off%20%5Ba%20practice%20of%5D%20aya%20ram%2C%20gaya%20ram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490703%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJyotiraditya%20Scindia.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40JM_Scindia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20margins%20in%20MP%20are%20thin.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP%20and%20managed%20to%20form%20the%20government%20after%20a%20hung%20assembly%20with%20the%20help%20of%20legislators%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20four%20independent%20MLAs.%20This%20ended%20the%20long%20rule%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chouhan%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%20BJP%20toppled%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20after%20almost%20two%20dozen%20Congress%20MLAs%20resigned%20and%20shifted%20to%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chouhan%20government%20not%20only%20faces%20the%20fatigue%20of%20ruling%20for%20almost%20two%20decades%20but%20also%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20set%20right%20in%20its%20house%2C%20as%20the%20defections%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAashish%20Joshi%2C%20director%20(admission)%20at%20the%20Makhanlal%20Chaturvedi%20National%20University%20of%20Journalism%20and%20Communication%2C%20says%20that%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20able%20to%20race%20ahead%20in%20the%20perception%20game%20by%20poaching%20some%20old%20and%20rooted%20BJP%20leaders.%20However%2C%20Chouhan%20has%20regained%20lost%20turf%20by%20announcing%20and%20implementing%20new%20schemes%20such%20as%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20programme%2C%20says%20Joshi.%20This%20has%20made%20it%20a%20tight%20contest%20as%20things%20stand%20today%2C%20he%20contends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20other%20factors%20yet%20to%20kick%20in%2C%20such%20as%20ticket%20distribution%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20how%20it%20handles%20possible%20discontent.%20Then%2C%20there%20is%20the%20Modi%20factor%20and%20his%20role%20in%20the%20campaigning.%20The%20Congress%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20was%20contesting%20the%20election%20with%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20CM%20candidate%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20he%20will%20contest%20the%20assembly%20election%20or%20choose%20the%20by-poll%20route%20like%20he%20did%20in%202018.%20His%20route%20to%20the%20CM%20chair%2C%20if%20his%20party%20wins%2C%20would%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20whether%20Chouhan%20would%20be%20the%20official%20CM%20candidate%20of%20the%20BJP.%20While%20these%20questions%20will%20be%20answered%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20pushed%20the%20BJP%20onto%20the%20backfoot%20in%20the%20perception%20game.%20And%20in%20elections%2C%20perception%20usually%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20always%20%E2%80%93%20dictates%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695175232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F29120555%2Fbjp-congress-manipur_pti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-internal-rift-congress-e