%20have%20also%20questioned%20the%20absence%20of%20sub-quotas%20in%20the%20legislation%20for%20women%20from%20OBC%20and%20Muslim%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20said%20that%20in%20the%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20conducted%20in%20India%20so%20far%2C%20over%208%2C000%20MPs%20have%20been%20elected%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20520%20have%20been%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20deficit%20of%2050%25.%20In%20the%20520%20only%20a%20handful%20are%20Muslim%20women.%20So%20who%20are%20you%20giving%20representation%3F%20Those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20representation%20should%20be%20given%20representation.%20The%20biggest%20flaw%20in%20this%20Bill%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20quota%20for%20OBC%20women%20and%20Muslim%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1704073157173498044%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EANI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sub-quota%20within%20the%20seats%20meant%20to%20be%20set%20aside%20for%20women%20was%20first%20vociferously%20articulated%20as%20a%20demand%20in%201996%2C%20when%20the%20United%20Front%20government%20discussed%20the%20case%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20state%20and%20central%20legislatures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20Mandal%20years%2C%20votaries%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20mostly%2C%20but%20also%20Dalit%20and%20tribal%20communities%2C%20felt%20that%20the%20stratification%20around%20the%20gender%20question%20was%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20movements%20to%20pitch%20caste%20and%20%E2%80%98backwardness%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20tentpole%20for%20marginalisation%20and%20underrepresentation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20advancing%20reservations%20for%20women%20before%20reserving%20seats%20for%20OBCs%2C%20they%20argued%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20women%20from%20forward%20castes%20and%20well-off%20communities%20would%20benefit.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reservations%20for%20women%20should%20have%20sub-quotas%20that%20account%20for%20social%20backwardness%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201997%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20%5BJD(U)%5D%E2%80%99s%20Sharad%20Yadav%20used%20the%20term%20%3Cem%3Epar-kati%20mahilaen%3C%2Fem%3E%20(short-haired%20women)%20in%20parliament%20to%20ask%20how%20short-haired%20or%20urban%20women%20would%20be%20able%20to%20represent%20%E2%80%9Cour%20women%E2%80%9D%2C%20implying%20women%20from%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMayawati%20extends%20support%2C%20SP%20to%20oppose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20president%20Mayawati%20said%20that%20her%20party%20will%20support%20any%20Bill%20that%20allows%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20Parliament%20and%20other%20legislatures%2C%20even%20if%20the%20demand%20for%20sub-quotas%20for%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20communities%20is%20not%20met.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E19-09-2023-BSP%20PRESS%20NOTE-WOMEN%20RESERVATION%20BILL%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6P9Z8Cb3eT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6P9Z8Cb3eT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mayawati%20(%40Mayawati)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMayawati%2Fstatus%2F1704065578435039358%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20stuck%20to%20its%20earlier%20position%20of%20opposing%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20PTI%2C%20Juhie%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20party%20respects%20women%20and%20sup