20allegations%20are%20serious%20and%20unprecedented%20in%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20history.%20However%2C%20they%20also%20warned%20against%20lumping%20India%20together%20with%20China%20and%20Russia%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20foreign%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStunning%2C%20says%20Globe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle-canada-is-once-more-thrust-into-a-new-world-of-foreign-intimidation%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20incident%20shows%20that%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20governments%20are%20continuing%20to%20reach%20into%20Canada%20to%20intimidate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20never%20been%20anything%20like%20this%20before%3A%20an%20explosive%20public%20allegation%20that%20a%20foreign%20government%E2%80%99s%20agents%20targeted%20and%20killed%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20in%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Campbell%20Clark.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20not%20supposed%20to%20be%20an%20enemy%2C%20or%20even%20an%20adversary%E2%80%9D%20despite%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20because%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20for%20decades%20%E2%80%9Caccused%20Canada%20of%20being%20soft%20on%20Khalistani%20terrorists%E2%80%9D.%20The%20report%20adds%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20often%20conflated%20non-violent%20Sikh%20separatist%20advocates%20with%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20the%20idea%20that%20New%20Delhi%20might%20send%20agents%20to%20kill%20a%20Canadian%20in%20Canada%20is%20%E2%80%9Cstunning%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20newspaper%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CCanada%20is%20jolted%20into%20recognizing%20a%20new%20world%20in%20which%20foreign%20governments%20reach%20out%20to%20influence%2C%20intimidate%20and%20coerce%20Canadians%20in%20Canada.%20Again%2C%20there%20is%20new%20reason%20to%20believe%20foreign%20interference%20might%20be%20a%20bigger%2C%20broader%20danger%20than%20this%20country%20is%20prepared%20to%20counter.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20allegation%20is%20assassination%2C%20which%20underlines%20the%20direct%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20of%20Canadians%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20those%20who%20belong%20to%20diaspora%20communities%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20refers%20to%20previous%20incidents%20of%20foreign%20interference%20in%20Canada%20such%20as%20illegal%20Chinese%20police%20activity%20in%20several%20Canadian%20locations%20and%20attempts%20by%20Beijing%20to%20influence%20Canadian%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cexplosive%2C%20albeit%20unproven%2C%20allegation%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20far%20from%20certain%20that%20the%20U.S.%20and%20other%20Canadian%20allies%20will%20rush%20to%20hold%20India%20to%20account%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20one%20thing%2C%20credible%20allegations%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20intelligence%20agencies%20aren%E2%80%99t%20the%20same%20as%20evidence%20gathered%20by%20police%20for%20a%20trial.%20And%20in%20a%20world%20where%20Western%20allies%20have%20imposed%20extensive%20economic%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20and%20are%20increasingly%20seeking%20to%20counter%20China%E2%80%99s%20influence%2C%20the%20U.S.%20and%20European%20nations%20won%E2%80%99t%20relish%20the%20prospect%20of%20conflict%20with%20another%20major%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20the%20allegation%20is%20true%2C%20it%20will%20be%20fuel%20for%20the%20coming%20public%20inquiry%20into%20foreign%20interference.%20Foreign%20governments%20apparently%20feel%20as%20though%20they%20can%20reach%20into%20Canada%20with%20impunity.%20Countering%20that%20is%20now%20a%20pressing%20national%20priority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Could%20be%20a%20significant%20setback%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnationalpost.com%2Fnews%2Fcanada-india-relations-enflamed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENational%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20claims%20are%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20the%20latest%20issue%20souring%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20much%20of%20which%20is%20centred%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20accusations%20that%20Canada%20has%20tolerated%20the%20growth%20here%20of%20a%20violent%20Khalistan%20independence%20movement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20Dehejia%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Carleton%20University%20who%20focuses%20on%20India%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20because%20of%20the%20Trudeau%20government%E2%80%99s%20continuing%20focus%20on%20catering%20to%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20voters%20%E2%80%9Cof%20the%20Sikh%20diaspora%20who%20are%20hostile%20to%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20historically%20important%20Liberal%20constituency%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintrinsically%20not%20very%20keen%20on%20(cozying)%20up%20with%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20could%20explain%20why%20the%20trade%20mission%20to%20India%20scheduled%20for%20the%20second%20week%20in%20October%20was%20abruptly%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Miller%2C%20senior%20fellow%20and%20director%20of%20foreign%20affairs%20at%20the%20Macdonald-Laurier%20Institute%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Canadian%20government%E2%80%99s%20accusations%20will%20%E2%80%9Cundoubtedly%20push%20relations%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%20even%20further%20apart%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20(allegation)%20is%20proven%2C%20if%20this%20incident%20sticks%2C%20I%20think%20this%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20setback%E2%80%A6%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20saying%20the%20relationship%20will%20never%20recover%2C%20or%20even%20in%20the%20medium%20term%20that%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20ways%20to%20get%20together%2C%20but%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20pretty%20large%20blow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMiller%20also%20cautioned%20against%20%E2%80%9Cputting%20India%20in%20the%20same%20foreign%20interference%20category%20as%20either%20Russia%20or%20China%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChina%20is%20head-over-heels%20a%20much%20larger%20threat%20actor%20for%20us%20in%20different%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20make%20the%20claim%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20%E2%80%9Crepresents%20a%20severe%20loss%20of%20face%20for%20the%20Indian%20government%20that%20will%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20repair%20relations%E2%80%9D%2C%20Miller%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19022725%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.30-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19022725%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.30-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19022725%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.30-AM-300x167.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19022725%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.30-AM-1024x571.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673616%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20scowls%20said%20it%20all.%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20their%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%20last%20week.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2FJustin%20Trudeau%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Violence%20must%20sto