20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19135234%2FNews-studio.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20early%20days%20as%20an%20expert%20invited%20to%20be%20a%20television%20commentator%2C%20I%20received%20valuable%20advice%20from%20Kashish%20Gupta%2C%20the%20anchor%20of%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Social%20Network%E2%80%9D.%20She%20suggested%20a%20straightforward%20approach%3A%20condense%20my%20points%20into%20three%20concise%20statements%2C%20each%20lasting%20no%20more%20than%20sixty%20seconds.%20This%20structure%20provided%20clarity%2C%20enabling%20me%20to%20prioritise%20information%20for%20the%20broader%20audience%E2%80%99s%20comprehension%20and%20persuasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelevision%20panels%2C%20I%20soon%20realised%2C%20are%20largely%20shaped%20by%20the%20anchor%20and%20the%20show%E2%80%99s%20format.%20While%20I%2C%20like%20many%2C%20was%20there%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20sentences%2C%20the%20anchor%20played%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20determining%20the%20topic%2C%20debate%20title%20and%20framing.%20In%20later%20years%2C%20even%20aspects%20like%20time%20allocation%20and%20audio%20levels%20became%20tools%20of%20manipulation%2C%20affecting%20the%20narrative%E2%80%99s%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJournalists%20inherently%20carry%20an%20opinion%2C%20a%20natural%20outcome%20of%20their%20chosen%20profession%E2%80%99s%20constant%20engagement%20with%20political%20matters.%20While%20some%20decry%20this%20%E2%80%9Cbias%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20contributes%20to%20media%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20should%20be%20tempered%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20reasoned%2C%20scientific%20inquiry%20to%20uncover%20the%20truth.%20In%20an%20ideal%20scenario%2C%20panel%20debates%20would%20feature%20clear%2C%20opposing%20positions%2C%20with%20the%20anchor%20moderating%20rationally.%20Yet%2C%20this%20often%20seems%20like%20a%20fantasy%2C%20and%20media%20entities%20in%20India%20historically%20served%20power%20and%20p