ese%20opportunities%2C%20he%20hatched%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20the%20people%20of%20Lucknow%20woke%20up%20to%20clarion%20calls%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKanyaon%20ki%20cricket%20hogi%2C%20zaroor%20aaiye%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Girls%20will%20be%20playing%20cricket%2C%20do%20come).%20The%20amplified%20voice%20belonged%20to%20none%20other%20than%20Sharma%2C%20who%20grouped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321379%2Fmaitrayana-uses-netball-sports-to-educate-and-empower-young-girls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterested%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20first%20association%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20in%20India.%20It%20was%20called%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20Association%20of%20India%20(WCAI)%20and%20was%20officially%20registered%20under%20the%20Societies%20Act%20of%20Lucknow%20in%201973.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20all-rounder%20in%20cricket%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%20was%20known%20for%20his%20leadership%20both%20on%20and%20off-field.%20A%20milestone%20feat%20in%20Dev%E2%80%99s%20career%20was%20captaining%20the%20Indian%20team%20that%20won%20the%201983%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20On%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%2C%20as%20he%20spoke%20to%20the%20team%20encouragingly%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20beat%20the%20mighty%20West%20Indies%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20highly%20doubted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20were%20proved%20wrong%2C%20as%20hours%20later%2C%20Dev%20lifted%20the%20trophy%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20skipper%20to%20do%20so.%20Recalling%20his%20pep%20talk%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20captain%2C%20you%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20if%20you%20rub%20those%20kinds%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321082%2Fgoa-katya-ida-coelho-first-indian-female-windfoiler-iqfoiler-qualifies-for-asian-games%2F%