0days%20at%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%20get%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%20tiger%20couple%20mating%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20honour%20for%20the%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20lessons%20that%20have%20stood%20him%20in%20good%20stead%20both%20in%20the%20wilderness%20and%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20photography%20journey%20is%20as%20compelling%20as%20his%20medical%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20trained%20under%20the%20renowned%20Dr%20Denton%20Cooley%20%E2%80%94%20famed%20for%20the%20first%20successful%20human%20heart%20transplant%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20interview%20he%20chanced%20upon%20in%20Class%209.%20Since%20then%2C%20matters%20of%20the%20heart%20held%20a%20fascination%20for%20him%20and%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back.%20Despite%20a%20lucrative%20career%20at%20the%20Cleveland%20Clinic%2C%20in%201993%2C%20Dr%20Ramakanta%20returned%20to%20India%20in%20an%20attempt%20%E2%80%9Cto%20offer%20the%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329080%2Fmission-icu-provides-critical-healthcare-facilities-to-rural-indian-hospitals-through-kits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20medical%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%E2%80%99s%20taken%20for%20granted%20overseas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20ask%20how%20pursuing%20a%20career%20in%20medicine%20allows%20time%20for%20hobbies%2C%20but%20Dr%20Ramakanta%20points%20out%20they%20expand%20the%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bphotography%5D%20has%20helped%20me%20focus%20better%20in%20my%20medical%20profession%20too.%20As%20you%20delve%20deeper%20into%20an%20unknown%20subject%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20look%20at%20life%20from%20a%20broader%20perspective%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%E2%80%99s%20majestic%20bird%20population%20of%20more%20than%201%2C300%20species%20compels%20him%20to%20venture%20into%20nature%20and%20get%20clicking.%20But%2C%20the%20numbers%20are%20dwindling%2C%20he%20warns.%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20protect%20and%20preserve