ographer-dr-ramakanta-panda-mumbai-heart-surgeon-pictures%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20IIT%20Delhi%20Alumni%20Help%20Educators%20Fight%20Piracy%20Through%20%E2%80%98Hollywood%20Grade%E2%80%99%20Security%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20VdoCipher%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202010%20and%202015%2C%20Siddhant%20Jain%20and%20Vibhav%20Sinha%20attended%20IIT%20Delhi.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20before%20the%20rise%20of%20OTT%20(over-the-top%20media%20service)%2C%20many%20students%20resorted%20to%20watching%20pirated%20movies%20and%20downloading%20pirated%20books%20and%20courses.%20Their%20awareness%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20piracy%20grew%20when%20they%20saw%20a%20close%20friend%20affected%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20roommate%20Satish%20used%20to%20teach%20chemistry%20to%20Class%2011%20and%2012%20students%20in%20Mathura%20and%20Delhi%20every%20weekend%20for%20a%20year.%20When%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301984%2Fjamtara-girl-ranks-upsc-cse-by-learning-from-youtube-videos-no-coaching-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20online%20coaching%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20popular%2C%20he%20thought%20of%20transitioning%20his%20classes%20online.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20sharing%20his%20carefully%20crafted%20notes%20online%2C%20fearing%20that%20his%20content%20might%20be%20leaked%20and%20distributed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatish%E2%80%99s%20quandary%20led%20the%20two%20friends%20to%20realise%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20that%20online%20video%20piracy%20was%20adversely%20affecting%20teachers%20like%20Satish%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20upload%20good%20content%20online.%20Many%20individuals%20would%20download%20these%20class%20videos%20and%20distribute%20them%20on%20platforms%20like%20Telegram%2C%20YouTube%20or%20WhatsApp%2C%20reaching%20a%20large%20audience.%20This%20situation%20resulted%20in%20genuine%20teachers%20losing%20the%20opportunity%20to%20enrol%20new%20students%20and%20losing%20income%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20piracy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20harm%20movie%20and%20show%20producers%3B%20it%20also%20impacts%20teachers%20and%20creators%20of%20educational%20content.%20Ultimately%20if%20teachers%20do%20not%20put%20their%20best%20content%20out%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20it%20is%20a%20loss%20to%20the%20student%20community%20as%20well.%20According%20to%20a%202022%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EAnkura%20Piracy%20Statistics%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20India%20ranks%20as%20the%20third-largest%20contributor%20to%20visits%20to%20content%20piracy%20websites%2C%20following%20the%20US%20and%20Russia%2C%20with%20over%20seven%20billion%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20while%20they%20were%20still%20students%2C%20these%20two%20engineers%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20solve%20this%20issue%20using%20their%20video%20encryption%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20security%20against%20online%20piracy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vibhav%20Sinha%20and%20Siddhant%20Jain%20founded%20VdoCipher%20in%202014%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977-500x26