%20where%20it%20is%20encrypted%2C%20ensuring%20access%20only%20to%20authorised%20users%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant%2C%20CEO%2C%20VdoCipher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20mobile%20phones%2C%20we%20can%20prevent%20screen%20capture%20also.%20Since%20this%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20prevented%20on%20computers%20in%20all%20cases%2C%20we%20provide%20user-based%20watermarking%20to%20discourage%20sharing.%20If%20they%20choose%20to%20share%20the%20screenshot%2C%20their%20name%2Fuser%20ID%20will%20appear%20on%20the%20image%3B%20it%20also%20helps%20us%20trace%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20duo%20claim%20to%20offer%20%E2%80%98Hollywood%20grade%20security%E2%80%99%20as%20they%20use%20the%20same%20technology%20used%20by%20Netflix%20and%20other%20large%20streaming%20services.%20Their%20USP%20is%20also%20their%20ability%20to%20provide%20this%20anti-piracy%20technology%20to%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20small%20teacher%20taking%20an%20online%20class%20to%20large%20ed-tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20Google%20DRM%20encryption%20and%20Apple%20DRM%20encryption%2C%20which%20provide%20very%20high%20security.%20They%20are%20the%20tools%20used%20by%20Netflix%2C%20Hollywood%20and%20Bollywood%20movies.%20We%20were%20the%20first%20company%20in%20India%20to%20provide%20such%20a%20high%20level%20of%20security%20technology%20in%20an%20easy-to-use%20way%2C%20notes%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20tech%20was%20not%20available%20to%20e-learning%20platforms%20as%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20integrate.%20We%20have%20made%20it%20easy%20and%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20government%20exam%20preparation%20course%20platform%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294819%2Futtar-pradesh-siblings-clear-upsc-cse-join-as-ias-ips-officers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E(UPSC%20and%20others)%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20over%2010%2C000%20online%20students%20and%2017%20centres%20across%20the%20country%20adds%20that%20their%20videos%20were%20getting%20leaked%20as%20the%20streaming%20platform%20was%20not%20secure.%C2%A0In%202019%2C%20they%20started%20using%20VdoCipher%E2%80%99s%20service%20and%20saw%20a%20marked%20difference%2C%20with%20more%20teachers%20trusting%20them.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CPartnering%20with%20VdoCipher%20stopped%20video%20sharing%20and%20helped%20us%20in%20brand%20building%20too.%20Teachers%20also%20developed%20confidence%20in%20our%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20security%2C%20VdoCipher%20also%20provides%20smooth%20streaming%20for%20slow%20internet%20connections%2C%20which%20helps%20premium%20content%20reach%20students%20in%20Tier%20II%20and%20III%20cities.%20VdoCipher%20also%20enables%20offline%20playback%20on%20mobiles%20and%20a%20bunch%20of%20interactive%20player%20features%20to%20ensure%20the%20best%20student%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20students%20from%20any%20remote%20areas%20in%20our%20country%20should%20get%20access%20to%20premium%20video%20content.%20Poor%20network%20connectivity%20should%20not%20be%20a%20hindrance%20in%20accessing%20quality%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVdoCipher%20uses%20a%20usage-based%20pricing%20model%20where%20customers%20pay%20based%20on%20how%20much%20data%20their%20students%20or%20viewers%20use.%20The%20duo%20claims%20to%20have%20over%203%2C000%20paying%20customers%20across%20100%20countries%2C%20streaming%20over%20seven%20million%20hours%20of%20content%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis.%20They%20say%20that%20as%20COVID%20led%20to%20a%20boom%20in%20the%20ed-tech%20space%2C%20the%20need%20for%20content%20security%20is%20also%20booming.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20seen%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20student%20footfall.%20This%20security%20has%20helped%20us%20do%20justice%20to%20serious%20students%2C%20teachers%20and