ed%20from%20browsers%2C%20we%20had%20to%20completely%20shift%20our%20technology%2C%20which%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20effort%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20faced%20hiccups%20in%20securing%20their%20initial%20funding%20as%20this%20space%20was%20relatively%20new%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20now%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20looking%20back!%E2%80%9D%20Currently%2C%20the%20engineers%20are%20assisting%20educators%20not%20just%20in%20India%20but%20also%20in%20other%20regions%20like%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300374%2Fjharkhand-principal-unique-blackboard-model-helps-village-children-and-elderly-study-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20physics%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Tunisia%2C%20Africa%2C%20who%20launched%20Tunisia%E2%80%99s%20first%20online%20course%20platform%2C%20is%20among%20their%20customers.%20Siddhant%20explains%20that%20when%20the%20teacher%20started%20using%20VdoCipher%20eight%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20200%20students.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20over%20four%20lakh%20students%20and%20over%20450%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20friend%20Satish%2C%20who%20inspired%20VdoCipher%2C%20is%20now%20a%20customer%20himself%20teaching%20chemistry%20through%20his%20coaching%20classes%20to%20students%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mondaq.com%2Findia%2Fmusic-and-the-arts%2F1280318%2Fmore-than-seven-billion-visits-to-content-piracy-websites-originated-from-india-in-2022--ankura-piracy-statistics-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnkura%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3